\id JOS
\h Yacuwa
\toc1 Yacuwa
\toc2 Yacuwa
\toc3 Yac.
\mt1 Yacuwa
\c 1
\s1 Řumur n SIDI i uṭeffu n temmurt n Kenɛan
\m 
\v 1 Awarni i řmewt n Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, issiweř SIDI ak-d Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, amsexxar n Musa, inna: \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Aɛwd. 34:5;1:38\x*
\v 2 “Musa, amsexxar inu immut. Řexxu kkar, ekk x L’Urdun-a, cek d marra řgens-a, ɣar temmurt i d asen ɣa wceɣ Necc, i ayt n Israil.
\v 3 Kuř amcan min xef ɣa teɛjen třeqqa n uḍar nwem, aqa wciɣ awem t i kenniw, am mammec i ssiwřeɣ Necc ak-d Musa. \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt Aɛwd. 11:24; Yac. 14:9\x*
\v 4 Tammurt nwem ad tiři zi řexřa ař Lubnan-a, ař iɣzar ameqqran, iɣzar n Lfuraṭ, marra tammurt n Iḥittiyyen ař Řebḥar Ameqqran \add ɣar řɣarb\add* mani tɣeǧi tfuct. \f ◼ \fr 1:4 \fk Řebḥar Ameqqran\ft - niɣ ‘Ill Ameqqran’. Řebḥar-a qqaren as di Arif ‘Řebḥar Ameẓyan’ u isem nnes n jdid aqa-t ‘Ill Agrakal’.\f*
\v 5 Uřa d ijj war izemmar ad iqqim ibedd zzat i wudem nnec marra ussan n tudart nnec. Am mammec d ayi tuɣa ak-d Musa, ad iřiɣ uřa akidek. Necc war dayek semmḥeɣ niɣ ad cek ttejjiɣ. \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt Aɛwd. 31:6, 8; Ɛbr. 13:5, 6\x*
\v 6 Iři d aryaz u iři tmeḥḍed, minzi cek ad tarred řgens-a ad iṭṭef tammurt d řwart, \add tammurt nni\add* x Necc jjuǧeɣ i řejdud nsen ad asen tt wceɣ. \x ◘ \xo 1:6 \xt Aɛwd. 31:23\x*
\v 7 Iři waha d aryaz u iři tmeḥḍed, maḥend ad teḥḍid ad tegged marra Ccariɛa nni d ac yumur Musa, amsexxar inu. War \add xas\add* ttḥeyyed \add ɣar\add* yefus uřa \add ɣar\add* uzeřmaḍ, maḥend ad tegged s řeɛqeř mani ma i ɣa traḥed. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Aɛwd. 5:32; 28:14\x*
\v 8 War ttejji ca adlis n Ccariɛa-ya ad ac ittwakkes x yiřes nnec, maca xarreṣ dayes ass d ǧiřet, maḥend ad teḥḍiḍ ad tegged ammu nican am mammec marra min dayes tura, minzi \add xenni\add* i ɣa tfeřḥed deg webrid nnec uca ad tt tegged s řeɛqeř. \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Izhd. 1:2\x*
\v 9 Ma war d ac t nniɣ? Iři d aryaz u iři tmeḥḍed, war tteggʷed u war ttejji ad iɛgez wuř nnec, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, aqa-t akidek qaɛ mani ma i ɣa traḥed.”
\m 
\v 10 Uca yumur Yacuwa i imeḥḍayen n řgens, inna:
\v 11 “Uyurem x řwesṭ n řmargeḥ n řɛeskar uca umur řgens, inim \add asen\add*: ‘Swejdet řeɛweč i yixef nwem, minzi awarni i třata n wussan ad teẓwam L’Urdun-a, ḥima ad tadfem ɣar temmurt i d awem ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d řwart uca ad tt teksim d řwart.’”
\m 
\v 12 Issiweř Yacuwa ak-d Irubiniyyen d Ijadiyyen u ak-d wezyen n teqbič n Manassa, inna:
\v 13 “Ɛeqřet x wawař nni x i d awem yumur Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, umi inna awem: ‘SIDI, AREBBI nwem, iwca awem arraḥet uca iwca awem tammurt-a.
\v 14 Timɣarin nwem, iḥenjiren nwem d řebhayem nwem ad qqimen di temmurt i d awem iwca Musa x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun uca kenniw ad teẓwam tḥezzmem zzat i wudem n aytmatwem, marra ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen, uca kenniw ad asen tewcem afus,
\v 15 ař ɣa yewc SIDI arraḥet i aytmatwem, am \add tuɣa iwca i\add* kenniw, uca uřa d nitni ad ṭṭfen tammurt i d asen iwca SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d řwart. \add Xenni\add* ad iɛeddeř ad dd-tdewřem ɣar temmurt tenni d řwart nwem uca ad twartem min d awem iwca Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun manis dd-tneqqar tfuct.”
\m 
\v 16 Nitni arrin-dd x Yacuwa, nnan: “Marra min xef i d aneɣ tumured, ad t negg u mani ma i d aneɣ ɣa tessekked, ad nuyur.
\v 17 Ammu nican am mammec nesřa ɣar Musa, ad ɣarek nseř. Mɣir iři ad kik yiři SIDI, AREBBI nnec, am mammec tuɣa iǧa ak-d Musa!
\v 18 Kuř aryaz nni i ɣa iɛṣan řumur nnec u war ixs ad iseř i wawařen nnec ɣar marra min d as ɣa tumured, ad ittwaneɣ. Iři waha d aryaz u iři tmeḥḍed!”
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Raḥab d tnayen n ibergagen
\m 
\v 1 Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, issekk zi Ciṭṭim tnayen n yeryazen maḥend ad bergagen s tnuffra, inna: “Uyurem, xzarem tammurt d Ariḥa!” Ffɣen, iwḍen ɣar taddart n ict n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř, qqaren as Raḥab, uca ssensen din.
\v 2 Xebbaren t i ujeǧid n Ariḥa, nnan: “Xzar, di ǧiřet-a usin-dd danita ca n yeryazen n ayt n Israil, ḥima ad bergagen di temmurt.”
\v 3 Issekk ujeǧid n Ariḥa ɣar Raḥab maḥend ad as inin: “Suffeɣ-dd iryazen i dd yudfen ɣar taddart nnem, minzi usin-dd, ḥima ad ksin řexbar x min ittemsaran di marra tammurt.”
\v 4 Aqa tessidef temɣart tnayen n yeryazen nni uca tessnuffar i-ten. Tenna: “S tidett, iryazen usin-dd ɣari, maca war ssineɣ manis nitni.
\v 5 Umi ttwabellɛent tewwura \add n tendint\add* ɣar uweṭṭu n taǧest, ffɣen yeryazen. Necc war ssineɣ mani uyuren yeryazen \add nni\add*. Ḍfarem ten deɣya, xenni tzemmarem ad xasen tḥartem.”
\m 
\v 6 \add Maca\add* nettat tessgeɛɛed i-ten x tzeqqa uca tessnuffar i-ten sadu iɣeddiwen n tiffest nni tuɣa ttwassarsen i nettat x tzeqqa.
\v 7 Tuɣa ten ḍeffaren yeryazen x webrid n L’Urdun ař imucan n uẓekkwu uca awarni řami ffɣen inni tuɣa ten iḍeffaren, bellɛen xasen tawwart.
\v 8 Qbeř i ɣa ṭṭṣen, tgeɛɛed \add Raḥab\add* ɣarsen ɣar tzeqqa,
\v 9 tenna asen: “Necc ssneɣ, aqa SIDI iwca awem tammurt-a u belli tiggʷudi zzaywem tewḍa-dd xaneɣ u marra imezdaɣ n temmurt fesyen deg wudem nwem.
\v 10 Maɣar neccin nesřa, mammec issiẓeɣ SIDI aman n Řebḥar n Telga deg wudem nwem umi dd-teffɣem zi Miṣra, uca \add nesřa ɛawed\add* min teggim ak-d Siḥun d Ɛuj, tnayen n ijeǧiden n Imuriyyen, inni tuɣa aɣirin i L’Urdun, inni tḥarrmem u tᵉtteḥḥam.\x ◘ \xo 2:10 \xt Uf. 14:21; Řxř. 21:24, 34; Yac. 4:23\x*
\v 11 \add Umi\add* nesřa aya, ifsiy wuř nneɣ, u war iqqim ca buḥbeř iddar di ca n yeryaz di ssibbet nwem, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d AREBBI, sennej deg ujenna d \add da\add* swadday x temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 2:11 \xt Aɛwd. 4:39\x*
\v 12 Řexxu \add xenni\add*, jjaǧem ayi ɣar SIDI, minzi necc ggiɣ zzaywem s tamexsiwt icewwaren, aqa uřa d kenniw ad teggem s tmexsiwt icewwaren ak-d \add řaǧ n\add* taddart n baba u wcem ayi ijj n weɛřam n řaman \add nwem\add*,
\v 13 aqa kenniw ad tejjem baba d yemma, aytma d suyᵉtma ak-d marra min iǧan nsen, ad ddaren u belli kenniw ad tfekkem řeɛmurat nneɣ zi řmewt.”
\m 
\v 14 Arrin-dd xas yeryazen: “Mařa war tefḍiḥem tamesřact nneɣ, ad immet řeɛmar nneɣ deg wemcan nwem. Uca ad imsar xmi d aneɣ ɣa iwc SIDI tammurt\add -a\add*, ad am nesscen tamexsiwt icewwaren d řaman \add nneɣ\add*.”
\m 
\v 15 Xas uca tseyyeb i-ten temɣart s yijj n wesɣun zi řkazi, minzi tuɣa taddart nnes ɣar řḥiḍ \add n barra\add* n wecbar \add n tendint\add* uca tuɣa tzeddeɣ deg wecbar \add n tendint\add*. *
\b
\m 
\v 16 Nettat tenna asen: “Ffɣem ɣar idurar, maḥend inni i kenniw iḍeffaren war xawem ḥarrten u ffarem dinni třata n wussan ař ɣa ɛeqben inni \add kenniw\add* iḍeffaren. Awarni man aya tzemmarem ad tmenɛem abrid nwem.”
\v 17 Iryazen nnan as: “Ad niři nettwassizdeg zi tjaǧit-a i d aneɣ teggid ad tt nejjaǧ,
\v 18 \add ila mařa ad tegged ammu:\add* Xzar, xmi i ɣa nadef ɣar temmurt, ittxeṣṣa ad tegged asɣun-a azeggʷaɣ imuden i zi d aneɣ tseyybed ɣar řkazi, uca ad tessmuned babam d yemmam d aytmam d marra řaǧ n babam ɣarem di taddart nnem.
\v 19 \add Maca\add* qaɛ wi ɣa iffɣen zi tewwura n taddart nnem, ad iřin idammen nnes x uzeǧif nnes, u neccin ad niři nettwassizdeg zzaysen, \add maca\add* qaɛ wenni akidem ɣa iqqimen di taddart, idammen nnes ad iřin x uzeǧif nneɣ mařa \add ca n yijj\add* ad xas issars afus. \x ◘ \xo 2:19 \xt Mt. 27:25\x*
\v 20 Mařa cem tessuffɣed tamesřact nneɣ, \add xenni\add* ad niři nettwassizdeg \add ɛawed\add* zi tjaǧit i d aneɣ teggid ad am nejjuǧ i cem.”
\v 21 Nettat tarra-dd xasen: “Ɛlaḥsab awařen nwem, ammu \add i ɣa yiři\add*!” \add Xenni\add* tejja i-ten ad uyuren uca tcedd asɣun azeggʷaɣ ɣar řkazi. \x ◘ \xo 2:21 \xt Ica. 1:18\x*
\m 
\v 22 Uyuren nitni uca iwḍen ɣar wedrar uca qqimen dinni třata n wussan, ařami dd-ɛeqben inni i ten iḍeffaren. Inni ten iḍeffaren tuɣa arezzun \add xasen\add* deg webrid marra, maca war \add ten\add* ufin.
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* areggʷḥen-dd tnayen nni n yeryazen, hwan-dd zeg wedrar, ẓwan-dd uca usin-dd ɣar Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, u ḥajan as marra min d asen imsaren.
\v 24 Nnan i Yacuwa: “S tidett, SIDI igga aneɣ marra tammurt deg ifassen u \add ɛawed\add* fesyen marra imezdaɣ n temmurt di ssibbet nneɣ.”
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Aẓwi n L’Urdun
\m 
\v 1 Ɣar tuffut zic, ikkar Yacuwa uca ksin iqiḍan nsen zi Ciṭṭim uca usin-dd ɣar L’Urdun, netta d marra ayt n Israil, uca ssensen dinni qbeř i ɣa ẓwan.
\v 2 Imsar awarni třata n wussan, aqa imeḥḍayen uyuren x řwesṭ n řmargeḥ n řɛeskar
\v 3 uca umuren řgens, nnan: “Xmi ɣa tẓarem Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, uca ikehhanen Ilawiyyen arbun tt, \add xenni\add* uřa d kenniw ad temmuṭṭyem zeg wemcam nwem, ad tt teḍfarem.
\v 4 Maca ittxeṣṣa ad tɛebbarem ttasiɛ ɛřaḥař i ařfayen n iɣaǧen jar awem d netta, war ɣares tadsem. Ammu i ɣa tessnem abrid i ɣa tekkem, maɣar kenniw \add zic\add* ɛemmarṣ war tekkim abrid-a, \add war iǧi\add* iḍennaḍ u \add war iǧi\add* fariḍennaḍ.”
\m 
\v 5 Inna Yacuwa i řgens: “Qeddsem ixef nwem, minzi tiwecca ad igg SIDI řeɛjayeb di řwesṭ nwem.”
\v 6 Issiweř Yacuwa \add ɛawed\add* ak-d ikehhanen, inna: “Sgeɛɛdem Ttabut n Řɛahd uca ẓwam zzat i wudem n řgens!” Nitni ssgeɛɛden Ttabut n Řɛahd u izwaren ɣar zzat i wudem n řgens.
\v 7 Tuɣa SIDI inna i Yacuwa: “Ass-a ad kkareɣ ad cek ssemɣareɣ zzat i tiṭṭawin n marra Israil, maḥend marra ad ssnen, aqa Necc akidek i ǧiɣ, am mammec i d ayi tuɣa ak-d Musa. \x ◘ \xo 3:7 \xt Yac. 1:5\x*
\v 8 Cek ad tumured ikehhanen inni yarebbun Ttabut n Řɛahd, ad tinid: ‘X minni i ɣa tawḍem ɣar tma n waman n L’Urdun, ad din tbeddem di L’Urdun!’”
\m 
\v 9 \add Xas uca\add* inna Yacuwa i ayt n Israil: “Asem-dd da u tesřem awařen n SIDI, AREBBI nwem.”
\v 10 Uca inna Yacuwa: “S man aya ad tessnem, aqa ijj n Arebbi iddar aqa-t jar awem u Netta ad issuffeɣ ayt n Kenɛan d Iḥittiyyen d Iḥiwiyyen d Ifariziyyen d Ijirjaciyyen d Imuriyyen d Iyabusiyyen zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem zi řwart nsen.
\v 11 Xzarem, Ttabut n Řɛahd n Sidi n marra tammurt tezwar awem zzat i wudem nwem di L’Urdun.
\v 12 Řexxu \add xenni\add*, farnem tenɛac n yeryazen zi tqebbař n Israil akidwem, ijj n weryaz zi kuř taqbič.
\v 13 Xmi iḍaren n ikehhanen, inni yarebbun Ttabut n SIDI, Sidi n marra tammurt, ad bedden deg waman n L’Urdun, \add xenni\add* ad imsar aqa aman n L’Urdun ad nqeḍɛen, aman i dd-ihekkwan zi sennej ɣar swadday, uca ad \add qqimen\add* bedden am yijj n weɣbar.” \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt Izhd. 114:3\x*
\v 14 \add Řami\add* ikkes řgens iqiḍan nnes ḥima ad iẓwa L’Urdun, arbun ikehhanen Ttabut n Řɛahd zzat i wudem n řgens. \x ◘ \xo 3:14 \xt Řex. 7:45\x*
\v 15 \add Umi\add* iwḍen iḥemmařen n Ttabut ɣar L’Urdun uca ḥadan iḍaren n ikehhanen, inni yarbun Ttabut, x tma n waman - tuɣa L’Urdun issfiy x marra tmewwa nnes di marra ussan n tmeyra - \x ◘ \xo 3:15 \xt 1 Im. 12:16\x*
\v 16 bedden waman nni dd-ihekkwan zi sennej. \add Aman\add* bedden nican am yijj n weɣbar iggʷej aṭṭas, ɣar tendint n Adam tenni zzat i Ṣartan. \add Ammu\add* i bedden \add waman\add* inni dd-ihekkʷan ɣar swadday, ɣar řebḥar n Řewḍa, ɣar Řebḥar Ameǧaḥ, aqa ttwaqeḍɛen qaɛ. \add Xenni\add* iẓwa řgens deg urendad n Ariḥa.
\v 17 Ikehhanen, inni yarbun Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI, bedden di řaman x řaẓaɣ, di řwesṭ n L’Urdun \add umi\add* iẓwa marra Israil x řaẓaɣ ařami ikemmeř marra řgens aẓwi x L’Urdun.
\b
\b
\c 4
\m 
\v 1 Umi tuɣa ikemmeř marra řgens aẓwi x L’Urdun, imsar aqa SIDI issiweř ak-d Yacuwa, inna: \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt Yac. 3:12\x*
\v 2 “Farnem tenɛac n yeryazen zi řgens, ijjen weryaz zi kuř taqbič,
\v 3 u tumured xasen, ini: ‘Ksim ssa, zi řwest n L’Urdun, zeg wemcan mani tuɣa bedden iḍaren n ikehhanen di řaman, tenɛac n iẓra, ksim ten akidwem ɣar ujemmaḍin, ssarsem ten di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar mani ɣa tessensem ǧiřet-a.’”
\m 
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa Yacuwa tenɛac n yeryazen nni ifarn i-ten zeg ayt n Israil, ijj n weryaz zi kuř taqbič,
\v 5 uca Yacuwa inna asen: “Uyurem zzat i wudem n Ttabut n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ɣar řwesṭ n L’Urdun uca ad iksi kuř aryaz i yixef nnes ijj n weẓru x teɣruḍt nnes, ɛlaḥsab řqedd n tqebbař n ayt n Israil,
\v 6 ḥima ad yiři aya d ict n řeɛřamet jar awem. Minzi \add mařa\add* iḥenjiren nwem ad sseqsan, ad inin: ‘Min \add ixs ad inin\add* yeẓra-ya i kenniw?’,
\v 7 \add xenni\add* kenniw ad asen tinim: ‘\add Aqa-ten din\add* minzi nqeḍɛen waman n L’Urdun zzat i wudem n Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI! Ɣar uẓwi x L’Urdun nqeḍɛen waman n L’Urdun uca iẓra-ya d ict n řidaret i ayt n Israil \add di man aya\add* i řebda.’” \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt Yac. 3:13\x*
\v 8 Ayt n Israil ggin am mammec tuɣa yumur Yacuwa uca ksin tenɛac n iẓra zi řwesṭ n L’Urdun, am mammec tuɣa issiweř SIDI ɣar Yacuwa, ɛlaḥsab řqedd n tqebbař n ayt n Israil, uca ksin ten akidsen ɣar ujemmaḍin, ɣar řmargeḥ mani tuɣa ssensen, uca ssarsen ten din.
\v 9 Issars Yacuwa \add ɛawed\add* tenɛac n iẓra di řwesṭ n L’Urdun, deg wemcan mani tuɣa mmarsen iḍaren n ikehhanen, inni yarbun Ttabut n Řɛahd, u aqa aten ɛad din ař ass-a.
\m 
\v 10 Ikehhanen, inni yarbun Ttabut, qqimen bedden di řwesṭ n L’Urdun, ařami tuɣa ittwakemmeř min inna SIDI i Yacuwa maḥend ad t yini i řgens ɛlaḥsab marra min yumur Musa i Yacuwa, uca iqeǧeq řgens ssenni, iẓwa.
\v 11 Umi tuɣa marra řgens ikemmeř aẓwi, teẓwa Ttabut n SIDI ak-d ikehhanen zzat i wudem n řgens.
\v 12 Ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad d wezyen n teqbič n Manassa ẓwan ḥezzmen i umenɣi zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil, am mammec tuɣa akidsen issiweř Musa. \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Řxř. 32:20, 29\x*
\v 13 Tuɣa-ten ɛřaḥař di arebɛin-ařef \add n yeryazen\add*, ḥezzmen \add marra\add* i umenɣi. Nitni ẓwan ɣar \add wazzay n\add* umenɣi zzat i wudem n SIDI, ɣar řewḍat n Ariḥa.
\v 14 SIDI issemɣar Yacuwa deg wass nni di tiṭṭawin n marra Israil uca ggʷeden zzayes am mammec tuɣa ggʷeden zi Musa, marra ussan n tudart nnes. \x ◘ \xo 4:14 \xt Yac. 3:7\x*
\m 
\v 15 SIDI issiweř ak-d Yacuwa, inna:
\v 16 “Umur i ikehhanen, inni yarebbun Ttabut n Cchadet, ad geɛɛden zi L’Urdun.”
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* yumur Yacuwa ikehhanen, inna: “Gaɛɛdem zi L’Urdun ɣar sennej!”
\v 18 Umi geɛɛden ikehhanen, inni yarbun Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI, zi řwesṭ n L’Urdun u tuɣa tisi n iḍaren n ikehhanen ɛad am mammec dd-ffɣen \add zeg waman\add*, imsar aqa aman n L’Urdun dewřen ɣar wemcan nsen uca dewřen ssfayen x marra timmawin nnes am yiḍennaḍ d fariḍennaḍ.
\v 19 Tuɣa řgens igeɛɛed zi L’Urdun deg wass wiss ɛecra deg uyur amezwaru uca wtin iqiḍan nsen di Jiljal, ɣar ccarq n Ariḥa.
\m 
\v 20 Di Jiljal issbedd Yacuwa tenɛac n iẓra i tuɣa akidsen-dd iksin zi L’Urdun.
\v 21 Uca netta issiweř ak-d ayt n Israil, inna: “Mařa sseqsan tiwecca iḥenjiren nwem ibabaten nsen uca ad inin: ‘Min \add xsen ad inin\add* yeẓra-ya?’
\v 22 \add xenni\add* ad tɛeřmem i iḥenjiren nwem, ad tinim: ‘\add Danita\add* iẓwa Israil L’Urdun-a x řaẓaɣ,
\v 23 minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem, issiẓeɣ aman n L’Urdun zzat i wudem nwem ařami teẓwam, am mammec i tuɣa igga SIDI, AREBBI nwem, \add ɛawed\add* ak-d Řebḥar n Telga nni issiẓeɣ zzat i wudem nneɣ ařami \add din\add* neẓwa, \x ◘ \xo 4:23 \xt Uf. 14:21\x*
\v 24 ḥima marra řegnus x temmurt ad ssnen, aqa afus n SIDI ijhed, ḥima kenniw ad teggʷdem SIDI, AREBBI nwem, i řebda.’”
\b
\b
\c 5
\s1 Axtan n řgens di Jiljal
\m 
\v 1 Umi marra ijeǧiden n Imuriyyen \add i iǧan\add* x tma n řɣarb n L’Urdun d marra ijeǧiden n ayt n Kenɛan \add i iǧan\add* ɣar řebḥar, sřan, aqa SIDI issiẓeɣ aman n L’Urdun zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil, ařami neẓwa ɣar ujemmaḍin, \add xenni\add* ifsiy wuř nsen u war daysen iqqim ca arruḥ zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil.
\v 2 Di řweqt nni issiweř SIDI ak-d Yacuwa: “Egg i yixef nnec ifarricen n weẓru uca xten i ayt n Israil i twařa wiss tnayen!” \x ◘ \xo 5:2 \xt Uf. 4:25\x*
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* igga Yacuwa ifarricen n weẓru i yixef nnes uca ixten i ayt n Israil ɣar Jibɛa-Haɛralut, \add aqa d ‘Tawrirt n Řeɛdařeyyat n Wextan’\add*.
\v 4 Man aya d řesbab i zi ixten i-ten Yacuwa: marra řgens i tuɣa dd-iffɣen zi Miṣra, \add marra\add* iwetman, \add ixs ad yini\add* marra iɛeskariyyen mmuten deg webrid di řexřa awarni i wuffuɣ nsen zi Miṣra.
\v 5 Minzi marra řgens nni dd-iffɣen, tuɣa-t ittwaxten, \add maca\add* marra řgens nni dd-ittwaxeřqen deg webrid di řexřa awarni i uffuɣ nsen zi Miṣra, nitni war ttwaxetnen ca. \x ◘ \xo 5:5 \xt Uf. 12:48\x*
\v 6 Minzi arebɛin n iseggʷusa gguren ayt n Israil di řexřa ařami ittwahellek řgens marra, marra iɛeskariyyen i tuɣa dd-iffɣen zi Miṣra, inni tuɣa war isřin ɣar tmijja n SIDI \add d inni\add* tuɣa ijjuǧ asen SIDI, war ten ittejji ca ad ẓaren tammurt nni x tuɣa ijjuǧ SIDI i řejdud nsen ad asen tt iwc, ict n temmurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment. \x ◘ \xo 5:6 \xt Řxř. 14:23\x*
\v 7 Iḥenjiren nsen inni issnekkar Netta deg wemcan nsen, d ina d inni tuɣa ixten Yacuwa, minzi nitni ɣarsen ɛad řeɛdařyet minzi war d asen xetnen deg webrid.
\v 8 Umi kemmřen ad xten marra řgens, imsar belli qqimen deg wemcan nsen di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar ařami ggenfan.
\v 9 Inna SIDI i Yacuwa: “Ass-a aqa kkseɣ xawem řefḍiḥet n Miṣra.” \add X uyenni\add* qqaren as i wemcan nni Jiljal, ař ass-a.
\b
\s1 Taɣarṣt n Useɛdu - ‘Manna’, aɣrum n ujenna, ibedd
\m 
\v 10 Wtin ayt n Israil iqiḍan nsen di Jiljal uca sswejden \add Taɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu deg wass arbeɛṭac n uyur \add nni\add*, di ǧiřet, di řewḍat n Ariḥa. \x ◘ \xo 5:10 \xt Uf. 12:6\x*
\v 11 Nitni ccin aɣrum břa antun d teɣwawin icennfen zi řɣiǧet n temmurt, zi tiwecca awarni i \add Taɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu, deg wass nni simant nnes. \x ◘ \xo 5:11 \xt Uf. 12:39; Lawi 2:14\x*
\v 12 Tiwecca nnes, awarni řami ccin zi řɣiǧet n temmurt, inneqḍeɛ manna. Ssenni war iqqim ɛad ‘manna’ i ayt n Israil. Deg useggʷas nni ccin zi řɣiǧet n temmurt n Kenɛan.
\b
\s1 Yacuwa iẓra Ameqqran n řɛeskar n SIDI
\m 
\v 13 Umi tuɣa iǧa Yacuwa zzat i Ariḥa, issgeɛɛed tiṭṭawin nnes, uca xzar, tuɣa ijj n weryaz ibedd zzates, ɣares ssif nnes deg ufus nnes. Yacuwa iruḥ ɣares inna as: “Cek ma zzayneɣ niɣ zeg iɣrimen nneɣ?” \x ◘ \xo 5:13 \xt Uf. 23:23\x*
\v 14 Netta yarra-dd: “Lla, minzi necc d akumandar n řɛeskar n SIDI. Necc řexxu i dd-usiɣ!” Uca iwḍa Yacuwa x uɣembub nnes ɣar temmurt, yuḍar, uca inna as: “Min ixs ad yini Sidi inu i umsexxar nnes?”
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* inna akumandar n řɛeskar n SIDI i Yacuwa: “Kkes tisiřa nnec zeg iḍaren nnec, minzi amcan i xef tbedded d amqeddas \add i iǧa\add*.” Uca amenni i igga Yacuwa. \x ◘ \xo 5:15 \xt Uf. 3:5\x*
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Aweṭṭu n Ariḥa
\m 
\v 1 Ariḥa tuɣa teqqen \add tiwwura nnes\add* nican zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil. Uřa d ijj war izemmar ad iffeɣ, uřa d ijj war izemmar ad \add din\add* yadef.
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Yacuwa: “Xzar, Necc ggiɣ ac Ariḥa ak-d ujeǧid nnes, ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen, deg ufus nnec.
\v 3 Ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad tennḍem i tendint. Marra iɛeskariyyen ad nnḍen i tendint ict n twařa. Amya i ɣa teggem setta n wussan.
\v 4 Sebɛa n ikehhanen ad izwaren zzat i Ttabut ad arbun sebɛa n waccawen n icarri i usřiwřew. Deg wass wiss sebɛa ad tennḍem i tendint sebɛa n twařawin u \add xenni\add* ad suḍen ikehhanen deg waccawen n icarri.
\v 5 Xmi ɣa yiři ijj n usuḍi d azirar deg yicc n usřiwřew u kenniw ad tesřem řḥess-a n usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri, \add xenni\add* ad yarreẓ řgens imun s tɣuyyit deg ujenna. Xas uca ad iwḍa řḥiḍ n tendint uca ad xas iẓwa řgens, kuř ijj n weryaz ad yuyur nican ɣar zzat.”
\m 
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, x ikehhanen, inna asen: “Ksim kenniw Ttabut n Řɛahd u ttejjem sebɛa n ikehhanen ad izwaren ɣar zzat i wudem n Ttabut n SIDI ad arbun sebɛa n waccawen n icarri i usřiwřew.”
\v 7 Nnan i řgens: “Ẓwam u tennḍem i tendint. Jjem iɛeskariyyen s řesnaḥ ad ẓwan zzat i wudem n Ttabut n SIDI.”
\m 
\v 8 Imsar am mammec tuɣa inna Yacuwa i řgens. Sebɛa n ikehhanen tuɣa arebbun sebɛa n waccawen n icarri i usřiwřew uca ẓwan zzat i wudem n SIDI, suḍen deg waccawen n icarri uca Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI teggur awarni asen.
\v 9 \add Iryazen\add* iḥezzmen s řesnaḥ izwaren zzat i wudem n ikehhanen nni isuḍen deg waccawen n icarri u x ḍeffar n Ttabut yusa-dd uɣezdis aneggaru \add n řɛeskar\add*, am gguren, ttsuḍen nitni deg waccawen n icarri.
\m 
\v 10 Yacuwa aqa yumur řgens, inna “War ttesɣuyyum, war ttejjim tmijja nwem ad as iseř ḥed, war dd-itteffeɣ uřa d ijj n wawař zeg uqemmum nwem ař ass nni d awem ɣa iniɣ: ‘Sɣuyyem!’ \add Xenni\add* ad tesɣuyyem i umenɣi.”
\v 11 Xas uca yejja Ttabut n SIDI ad tenneḍ i tendint, ict n twařa tenneḍ as-dd. \add Xenni\add* dewřen ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, ssensen di řmargeḥ.
\v 12 Tiwecca nnes ɣar tuffut n zic ikkar Yacuwa uca arbun ikehhanen Ttabut n SIDI.
\v 13 Sebɛa n ikehhanen nni tuɣa yarebbun sebɛa n waccawen n icarri i usřiwřew zzat i wudem n Ttabut n SIDI, qqimen gguren, suḍen deg waccawen n icarri u \add iryazen\add* iḥezzmen s řesnaḥ izwaren ɣar zzat u x ḍeffar n Ttabut n SIDI iḍfar uɣezdis aneggaru \add n řɛeskar\add*, am \add qqimen\add* gguren am ttsuḍen deg waccawen n icarri.
\v 14 Deg wass wiss tnayen nnḍen \add ɛawed\add* ict n twařa i tendint uca dewřen ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar. Ammu i ggin setta n wussan.
\v 15 Deg wass wiss sebɛa, imsar, aqa kkaren zic, umi iṣbeḥ řḥař, uca nnḍen ammu sebɛa n twařawin i tendint. Deg wass nni waha nnḍen i tendint sebɛa n twařawin.
\v 16 Uca imsar ɣar twařa wiss sebɛa umi suḍen ikehhanen deg waccawen n icarri, aqa Yacuwa inna i řgens: “Sɣuyyem, minzi SIDI igga awem tandint deg ufus!
\v 17 Tandint ad tᵉttwaḥarrem i SIDI, tandint d marra min dayes. Mɣir tamɣart n farq-ccɣeř Raḥab waha d marra inni ɣares iǧan di taddart nnes ad qqimen ddaren, minzi nettat tessnuffar x ireqqasen nni tuɣa nessekk.
\v 18 Ḥḍam ixef nwem zi marra min ittwaḥarrmen, maḥend kenniw war teddikkwiřem d ayt n řeḥram \add am\add* teksim \add ca\add* n min iǧan d řeḥram u ad tarrem řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Israil d řeḥram u ad t tɣeḍřem d arrẓiyet.
\v 19 Marra nnuqart d wureɣ d řeqcuɛ n nnḥas d wuzzař, \add marra aya\add* d amqeddas i SIDI uca ad t tessidfem deg wexxam n txubay n SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 6:19 \xt Řxř. 31:54\x*
\v 20 Xas uca isɣuy řgens i umenɣi uca suḍen deg waccawen n icarri. Uca imsar, umi isřa řgens řḥess n usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri, aqa řgens yarreẓ deg ict n tɣuyyit deg ujenna u řḥiḍ n tendint ihdem u řgens igeɛɛed, yudef ɣar tendint, kuř ijj n weryaz yuyur nican ɣar zzat, uca ṭṭfen nitni tandint. \x ◘ \xo 6:20 \xt Ɛbr. 11:30\x*
\v 21 Ḥarrmen marra min iǧan di tendint i řḥukm s řeqḍeɛ n ssif, zeg iryazen ař timɣarin, zeg iḥramen ař iwessura, ař afunas, uǧi d weɣyuř.
\v 22 Inna Yacuwa i tnayen n yeryazen nni tuɣa ittbergagen tammurt: “Adfem ɣar taddart n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř, u ssuffɣem tamɣart nni ak-d marra min ɣares, am mammec kenniw i d as tejjuǧem.” \x ◘ \xo 6:22 \xt Yac. 2:14; Ɛbr. 11:31\x*
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* udfen ibřiɣen, ibergagen, uca ssuffɣen-dd Raḥab ak-d babas d yemmas d aytmas d marra min iǧan nnes. Ssuffɣen marra řaǧ nnes uca ggin asen mani ɣa qqimen barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Israil.
\v 24 Sscemḍen tandint d marra min dayes s tmessi. Mɣir nnuqart d wureɣ d řeqcuɛ n nnḥas d wuzzař, ssidfen ten ɣar wexxam n txubay di Taddart n SIDI.
\v 25 Raḥab, tamɣart n farq-ccɣeř d \add řaǧ n\add* taddart n babas d marra min iǧan nnes, ijja i-ten Yacuwa ad ddaren. U nettat tzeddeɣ di řwesṭ n Israil ař ass-a, minzi tuɣa tessnuffar x ireqqasen i tuɣa issekk Yacuwa, ḥima ad bergagen tammurt.
\v 26 Di řweqt nni ijjuǧ Yacuwa, inna: “Aryaz nni i ɣa issbedd Ariḥa ɛawed ad yiři ittwanɛeř zzat i wudem n SIDI. Ad as yegg dsas nnes di tareẓẓit n umenzu nnes, ad issbedd tiwwura nnes di tareẓẓit n mmis amaẓuẓ.” \x ◘ \xo 6:26 \xt 1 Ij. 16:34\x*
\v 27 \add Ammu\add* i tuɣa SIDI ak-d Yacuwa, uca řexbar ikka marra tammurt.
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Ddenb n Ɛaxan
\m 
\v 1 Ayt n Israil ɣeccen ak-d min iǧan ittwaḥarrmen \add i uteḥḥi\add*. Ɛaxan, mmis n Karmi, mmis n Zabdi, mmis n Zaraḥ, zi teqbič n Yahuda, iksi ca zi min ittwaḥarrmen \add i uteḥḥi\add*. \add Xenni\add* yarɣa weɣḍab n SIDI x ayt n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 7:1 \xt Yac. 22:20; 1 Im. 2:7\x*
\m 
\v 2 Yacuwa issekk iryazen zi Ariḥa ɣar Ɛay i iǧan ɣar Bayt-Awin, ɣar ccarq n Bayt-Il. Netta issiweř akidsen, inna: “Gaɛɛdem, bergagem tammurt!” Iryazen ffɣen u bergagen x Ɛay.
\v 3 \add Umi\add* dd-ɛeqben ɣar Yacuwa, nnan as: “Nhřa ma igeɛɛed din marra řgens. Ejj ad geɛɛden din ɛřaḥař ařfayen niɣ teřt-ařaf n yeryazen ḥima ad ɣeřben x Ɛay. War dd-ttiwyed ca dinni marra řgens, minzi nitni aqa aten di drus.
\v 4 \add Ammu\add* i geɛɛden zi řgens ɛřaḥař teřt-ařaf n yeryazen, \add maca\add* nitni arewřen zzat i wudem n yeryazen n Ɛay.
\v 5 Iryazen n Ɛay nɣin zzaysen setta u-třatin n yeryazen uca ḍfaren ten zi zzat n wudem n tewwart ař Cabarim uca ɣeřben xasen deg uhekkwu. \add Xenni\add* ifsiy wuř n řgens, idweř am waman.
\m 
\v 6 Yacuwa icarreg arruḍ nnes, iwḍa x uɣembub nnes ɣar temmurt zzat i Ttabut n SIDI, ař ǧiřet, netta d imɣaren n Israil, uca nitni ssuyusen ucař x uzeǧif nsen.
\v 7 Yacuwa inna: “A, Sidi inu, SIDI, mayemmi tejjid řgens-a ad iẓwa L’Urdun? Ma ḥima ad aneɣ tegged deg ufus n ayt n Imuriyyen, maḥend ad aneɣ teḥḥan? Iři, negga ad neqbeř ad nezdeɣ ɣar ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun.”
\v 8 A Sidi inu, min ɣa iniɣ, awarni i umi yarra Israil aɛrur ɣar wudem n řɛedyan nnes \add maḥend ad yarweř\add*?
\v 9 Mařa ad t sřen ayt n Kenɛan d marra imezdaɣ n temmurt, ad aneɣ qewwaren, ad qeḍɛen isem nneɣ zi tammurt. Min i ɣa tegged \add xenni\add* i Yisem nnec ameqqran?”
\m 
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Yacuwa: “Kkar, mayemmi \add da\add* tmedded ammu x uɣembub nnec ɣar temmurt?
\v 11 Aqa Israil ixḍa uca nitni ɛeddan Řɛahd inu nni x d asen umureɣ. Ksin \add ɛawed\add* zi min iǧan ittwaḥarrmen \add i uteḥḥi\add*, ucaren \add ɛawed\add*, ssxarrqen \add ɛawed\add* uca ssarsen \add aya\add* \add ɛawed\add* ɣar řeqcuɛ nsen.
\v 12 \add X uya\add* war zemmaren ayt n Israil ad qqimen bedden zzat i wudem n řɛedyan nsen. Ad arrin aɛrur ɣar wudem n řɛedyan nsen \add maḥend ad arewřen\add*, minzi nitni dewřen ttwaḥarrmen \add qaɛ\add* i lḥukm. Necc war kiwem ttiřiɣ ɛad, mařa war tekksem zi řwesṭ nwem min ittwaḥarrmen \add i uteḥḥi\add*.
\v 13 Kkar, sqeddes řgens, ad tinid: ‘Sqeddsem ixef nwem i tiwecca, minzi ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: Aqa din ca min ittwaḥarrmen \add i uteḥḥi\add* di řwesṭ nwem, Israil! War tzemmared ad tessbedded řɛedyan nnec, ař ɣa tekksem zi řwesṭ nwem min ittwaḥarrmen \add i uteḥḥi\add*.
\v 14 Tiwecca ad dd-tqarrbem, \add ad tiřim tᵉttwasettfem\add* ɛlaḥsab tiqebbař nwem uca \add xenni\add* ad dd-tqarreb teqbič nni iɛeǧem SIDI, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat \add nnes\add* u řaǧ i ɣa iɛeǧem SIDI ad dd-iqarreb ɛlaḥsab \add řaǧat n\add* tudrin \add nnes\add* uca \add řaǧ n\add* taddart nni i ɣa iɛeǧem SIDI ad dd-iqarreb \add am ttwasettfen nitni\add* ɛlaḥsab \add iryazen\add* ibřiɣen \add nsen\add*.
\v 15 Uca ad imsar, aqa wenni iksin ca zi min ittwaḥarrmen \add i uteḥḥi\add* ad ittwassecmeḍ s tmessi ak-d marra min ɣares iǧan, minzi netta iɛedda x Řɛahd n SIDI u igga řefḍiḥet di Israil.’”
\m 
\v 16 Ikkar Yacuwa zic uca ijja ad dd-isqarreb Israil taqbič taqbič uca tᵉttwaɛeǧem teqbič n Yahuda.
\v 17 Ijja ad dd-tqarreb řaǧ n Yahuda uca tᵉttwaɛeǧem řaǧ n Izaraḥiyyen. \add Xenni\add* ijja ad dd-tqarreb řaǧ n Izaraḥiyyen, \add tᵉttwasettef\add* ɛlaḥsab \add iryazen\add* ibřiɣen \add nnes\add* uca ittwaɛeǧem Zabdi.
\v 18 Netta ijja ad dd-iqarreb \add řaǧ n\add* taddart nnes, \add am ttwasettfen nitni\add* ɛlaḥsab \add iryazen\add* ibřiɣen \add nsen\add*, uca ittwaɛeǧem Ɛaxan, mmis n Karmi, mmis n Zabdi, mmis n Zaraḥ, zi teqbič n Yahuda.
\m 
\v 19 Yacuwa inna i Ɛaxan: “A mmi, ewc řɛezz i SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, u qada i-t! Ini ayi, min teggid cek, war xafi snuffar ca”
\v 20 Ɛaxan yarra-dd x Yacuwa, inna: “Aqa s tidett, necc xḍiɣ ak-d SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, \add maɣar\add* necc ggiɣ ta d ta.
\v 21 Necc ẓriɣ jar tkeccaḍt ijj n upartessu izewwqen zi Cinar d mitayen ciqlu n nnuqart d ict n tbarrat n wureɣ tewzen xemsin ciqlu. Necc meẓreɣ daysen uca iwyeɣ ten-dd ɣari, aqa aten nnufaren di temmurt, di řwesṭ n uqiḍun inu, d nnuqart swadday.”
\v 22 Yacuwa issekk ireqqasen. Nitni uzzřen ɣar uqiḍun, xzar, \add řeḥwayej\add* tuɣa aten nuffaren deg uqiḍun, d nnuqart swadday.
\v 23 Ksin nitni \add řeḥwayej nni\add* zi řwesṭ n uqiḍun uca iwyen ten ɣar Yacuwa u ɣar marra ayt n Israil uca ssarsen ten zzat i wudem n SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 7:23 \fk ssarsen ten ...\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘seyyben ten’.\f*
\m 
\v 24 Yacuwa, d marra Israil akides, iksi Ɛaxan, mmis n Zaraḥ, uřa d nnuqart d upartessu izewwqen d tbarrat n wureɣ d iḥenjiren nnes d yessis nnes d ifunasen nnes d iɣyař nnes d wuǧi nnes d uqiḍun nnes d marra min ɣares uca iwyen ten ɣar teɣzurt n Axur.
\v 25 Inna Yacuwa: “Mayemmi d aneɣ teggid di arrẓiyet? SIDI ad cek yegg di arrẓiyet ass-a!” D marra Israil yarjem i-t s iẓra uca sscemḍen ten s tmessi uca nḍaren xasen iẓra.
\v 26 Ssbedden xas ijj n uɛurric d ameqqran n iẓra \add wenni din iǧan\add* ař ass-a. Uca SIDI igga ad dd-iɛqeb řḥaduq n weɣḍab nnes. X uya qqaren as i temmurt nni: ‘Taɣzurt n Axur’ ař ass-a. \f ◼ \fr 7:26 \fk Axur\ft - min ixs ad yini ‘řeɣben’.\f*
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Aɣelleb x Ɛay
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Yacuwa: “War tteggʷed, war ttejji ad iɛgez wuř nnec. Ksi akidek marra řgens n řɛeskar, kkar, tuyured ɣar Ɛay! Xzar, Necc ggiɣ ajeǧid n Ɛay d řgens nnes d tendint nnes d temmurt nnes deg ufus nnec. \x ◘ \xo 8:1 \xt Aɛwd. 1:21; 7:18\x*
\v 2 Cek ad tegged ak-d Ɛay u ak-d ujeǧid nnes am mammec teggid ak-d Ariḥa u ak-d ujeǧid nnes, ad teksim mɣir takeccaḍt d řebhayem waha i yixef nwem. Egg deg weɛrur n tendint ijn n řfex.” \x ◘ \xo 8:2 \xt Aɛwd. 20:14; Yac. 6:21\x*  *
\b
\m 
\v 3 \add Xas uca\add* ikkar Yacuwa ak-d marra řgens n řɛeskar ḥima ad igeɛɛed ɣar Ɛay. Ixḍar Yacuwa teřt-ařaf n yeryazen, ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen, uca issekk i-ten s ǧiřet
\v 4 uca yumur i-ten, inna: “Xzarem, ad teggem řfex ɣar weɛřuř n tendint. War tiggʷejem aṭṭas x tendint u iřim tḥezzmem.
\v 5 Necc ad dd-qarrbeɣ ɣar tendint ak-d marra řgens. Ad imsar mařa ffɣen i umsagar akidneɣ am \add twařat\add* tamezwarut, \add xenni\add* ad zzaysen narweř zzat i wudem nsen.
\v 6 Nitni ad aneɣ dd-ḍfaren ař ten dd-nessiggʷej x tendint, minzi nitni ad inin: ‘Nitni arewřen zzat i wudem nneɣ am \add twařat\add* tamezwarut.’ \add Xmi\add* zzaysen ɣa narweř zzat i wudem nsen,
\v 7 ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad tekkarem zeg wecbar, ad tᵉṭṭfem tandint, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ad tt iwc deg ufus nwem.
\v 8 Uca ad imsar x minni i ɣa tiři tᵉṭṭfem tandint, ad tessarɣem tandint s tmessi. Ittxeṣṣa ad teggem ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI. Xzarem, necc aqa umureɣ kenniw.”
\m 
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* issekk i-ten Yacuwa uca nitni ggin řfex uca qqimen jar Bayt-Il d Ɛay, ɣar řɣarb x Ɛay. Yacuwa issens ǧiřet nni di řwesṭ n řgens.
\v 10 Tiwecca zic ikkar Yacuwa. Iḥseb řgens \add i umenɣi\add* uca igeɛɛed ak-d imɣaren n Israil zzat i wudem n řgens ɣar Ɛay.
\v 11 Marra řgens n řɛeskar, inni kis iǧan, iffeɣ-dd uca nitni qarrben-dd uca iwḍen ař qibač i tendint. Nitni wtin iqiḍan nsen ɣar ccamal n Ɛay. Tuɣa \add din\add* ict n teɣzurt jar as-dd d Ɛay.
\v 12 Iksi netta ɛřaḥař xemsa-ařaf n yeryazen uca igga asen řfex jar Bayt-Il d Ɛay, ɣar řɣarb n tendint.
\v 13 Ssbedden řgens, zeɛma marra řɛeskar ɣar ccamal n tendint, uca aɣezdis aneggaru \add n řɛeskar\add* ɣar řɣarb n tendint. Yacuwa iruḥ ǧiřet nni ɣar řwesṭ n řewḍa n teɣzurt.
\m 
\v 14 \add Umi\add* iẓra-ya ujeǧid n Ɛay, qeǧqen uca kkaren zic. Ffɣen iryazen n tendint i umsagar ak-d Israil, i umenɣi, netta ak-d marra řgens nnes, ɣar wazzay \add n umenɣi\add* zzat i wudem n Řewḍa. Maca netta war issin belli tuɣa ggin as ijj n řfex ɣar weɛrur n tendint.
\v 15 Yacuwa d marra Israil ggin axmi jjin ixef nsen ad ttwawten qibač nsen uca arewřen x webrid n řexřa.
\v 16 Marra řgens i tuɣa iǧan di tendint řaɣan ten ḥima ad ten ḍfaren. Ḍfaren Yacuwa uca dewřen iggʷejen x tendint.
\v 17 Uřa d ijj n weryaz war iqqim di Ɛay niɣ di Bayt-Il, wenni war dd-iffiɣen ca i weḍfar awarni i Israil, uca nitni jjin tandint tarzem uca qqimen ḍeffaren \add ayt n\add* Israil.
\m 
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* issiweř SIDI ak-d Yacuwa: “Swiẓẓeḍ aḥric nni deg ufus nnec ɣar Ɛay, minzi Necc ad wceɣ tandint deg ufus nnec.” \add Xenni\add* isswiẓẓeḍ Yacuwa aḥric nni deg ufus nnes ɣar tendint. \f ◼ \fr 8:18 \fk Necc ad wceɣ tandint deg ufus nnec\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Necc ad tt wceɣ deg ufus nnec’.\f*
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* ikkar uɣezdis aneggaru \add n řɛeskar\add* deɣya uca umi isarreḥ \add Yacuɛa\add* afus nnes, bdan ad azzřen uca iwḍen ɣar tendint uca ṭṭfen tt. Ggin t s tazřa uca ssekkaren timessi di tendint.
\v 20 Iryazen n Ɛay nnqeřben uca ẓrin ddexxan yuři ɣar ujenna zi tendint. Nitni war zemmaren ad arewřen ɣar da uřa ɣar din, \add minzi\add* řgens i tuɣa yarewřen ɣar řexřa, inneqřeb-dd \add i umenɣi\add* x wenni ten iḍeffaren.
\v 21 \add Umi\add* iẓar Yacuwa d marra ayt n Israil belli \add inni tuɣa rajan di\add* tnuffra, ṭṭfen tandint uca yuři ddexxan zi tendint, ɛeqben-dd nitni uca wtin iryazen n Ɛay.
\v 22 Inni dd-iffɣen zi tendint, ruḥen i umsagar akidsen, ařami \add iryazen n Ɛay\add* dewřen di řwesṭ n Israiliyyen, ina ɣar uɣezdis-a d ina ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni, uca nitni ɣeřben xasen ařami war zzaysen iqqim uřa d ijjen ad yarweř niɣ ad injem. \x ◘ \xo 8:22 \xt Aɛwd. 7:2\x*
\v 23 Menɛen ajeǧid n Ɛay am iddar \add ɛad\add* u iwyen t ɣar Yacuwa.
\m 
\v 24 \add Umi\add* ayt n Israil kemmřen ad nɣen marra imezdaɣ n Ɛay, \add am\add* deg iyyar \add am\add* di řexřa mani tuɣa ten dd-ḍfaren uca ttwanɣen marra s řeqḍeɛ n ssif, \add xenni\add* iɛqeb Israil ɣar Ɛay uca wtin tt s řeqḍeɛ n ssif.
\v 25 Marra inni ittwanɣen deg wass nni, iryazen d temɣarin, tuɣa aten di tenɛac-ařaf, dayes marra iryazen n Ɛay.
\v 26 Yacuwa war issehwi afus nnes i isswiẓẓḍen s uḥric ařami tuɣa iḥarrem marra imezdaɣ n Ɛay \add i uteḥḥi\add*.
\v 27 Ksin Israiliyyen mɣir řebhayem d tkeccaḍt n tendint nni i yixef nsen ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI, \add awař\add* nni yumur Netta i Yacuwa. \x ◘ \xo 8:27 \xt Řxř. 31:22, 26; Yac. 8:2\x*
\v 28 Issecmeḍ Yacuwa \add tandint n\add* Ɛay uca yarra i-tt d ict n řxirbet i řebda, d ict n temmurt d řexřa ař ass-a.
\v 29 Netta yuyeř ajeǧid n Ɛay ɣar ict n teḥnact ař tameddit u umi teɣři tfuct, yumur Yacuwa ad kksen řxecbet nnes zi teḥnact. Nḍaren tt ɣar wadaf n tewwart n tendint u ssbedden xas ijj n uɛurric d ameqqran n yeẓra, \add i din iǧan\add* ɛad ař ass-a. \x ◘ \xo 8:29 \xt Aɛwd. 21:22, 23\x*
\b
\s1 Aɛaltar x wedrar n Ibal d tɣuri n Ccariɛa
\m 
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* ibna Yacuwa ijj n uɛalṭar i SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, x wedrar n Ɛibal,
\v 31 am mammec \add t\add* yumur Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, i ayt n Israil, ɛlaḥsab min yuran deg wedlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa n Musa: ijj n uɛalṭar n weẓru qaɛ, war xas meyyřen s \add uřa d ijj n dduzan n\add* wuzzař zi ssa ɣar da. Nitni bexxaren xas tiɣarṣa n tmessi i SIDI. Ɣarṣen \add ɛawed\add* tiɣarṣa n řehna. \x ◘ \xo 8:31 \xt Uf. 20:25; Aɛwd. 27:4\x*
\v 32 X yeẓra igga netta ict n tiřemt n tira n Ccariɛa n Musa, tenni yura zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 8:32 \xt Aɛwd. 27:3\x*
\v 33 Marra ayt n Israil d imɣaren d imeḥḍayen d řquḍat bedden ɣar uɣezdis-a u ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni n Ttabut qibač i ikehhanen zi \add ayt n\add* Lawi inni yarbun Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI, am ubarrani am aytbab n temmurt. Azyen zzaysen tuɣa zzat n wedrar n Jirizim u azyen nneɣni ɣar zzat n wedrar n Ɛibal, am mammec tuɣa yumur Musa, amsexxar n SIDI zic, maḥend ad barken \add ammu\add* ayt n Israil.
\v 34 Awarni uya iɣra marra awařen n Ccariɛa, lbaraka d nneɛřet, ɛlaḥsab marra min yuran deg wedlis n Ccariɛa.
\v 35 Zi marra min tuɣa yumur Musa, war iǧi uřa d ijj n wawař, war t iɣri Yacuwa i marra agraw \add n řgens\add* n Israil, uřa d timɣarin d iḥenjiren imeẓyanen d ubarrani wenni akidsen iruḥen, \add tuɣa aten din\add*. \x ◘ \xo 8:35 \xt Aɛwd. 31:11\x*
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Taḥraymect n ayt n Jibɛun
\m 
\v 1 Umi marra ijeǧiden, inni yeǧan x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun ṣrin x man aya - \add ijeǧiden\add* x Temmurt n Idurar, di Temmurt Iwaṭan u ɣar marra tma n Řebḥar Ameqqran ař qibač i \add idurar n\add* Lubnan: Iḥittiyyen d Imuriyyen d ayt n Kenɛan d Ifariziyyen d Iḥiwiyyen d Iyabusiyyen -\f ◼ \fr 9:1 \fk Řebḥar Ameqqran\ft - niɣ ‘Ill Ameqqran’. Řebḥar-a qqaren as di Arif ‘Řebḥar Ameẓyan’ u isem nnes d jdid aqa-t ‘Ill Agrakal’.\f*
\v 2 munen nitni ḥima ad mmenɣen ak-d Yacuwa u ak-d Israil x ijj n array.
\v 3 \add Umi\add* imezdaɣ n Jibɛun sřin min tuɣa igga Yacuwa ak-d Ariḥa d Ɛay,
\v 4 ggin t s teḥraymect. Nitni uyuren deg webrid uca ggin ixef nsen d imsekkan. Iwyen tixuncay tibuřay x iɣyař nsen, tixuncay n yiřem tibuřay ttwacarrgent u twaxeyyḍent \add ɛawed\add* i binu.
\v 5 \add Qqnen ɛawed\add* tisiřa d řbari, ittwaḍarrfen x iḍaren nsen u yarḍen arruḍ abuřay, u marra aɣrum n řeɛweč nsen tuɣa yuẓeɣ ittfruruy.
\m 
\v 6 Uyuren \add ammu\add* ɣar Yacuwa di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Jiljal, nnan as i netta u i ayt n Israil: “Neccin nusa-dd zeg ict n temmurt tiggʷej. Řexxu xenni, ggem ijj n řɛahd akidneɣ.”
\v 7 Arrin-dd iryazen n Israil x Iḥiwiyyen: “Ad taɣ kenniw tzeddɣem jar aneɣ. Mammec nzemmar ad kidwem negg ijj n řɛahd?”
\v 8 Nitni maca nnan i Yacuwa: “Neccin d imsexxaren nnec.” \add Xenni\add* inna asen Yacuwa: “Min teɛnam kenniw d manis i dd-tusim?”
\v 9 Nitni arrin-dd xas: “Imsexxaren nnec usin-dd zeg ict n temmurt tiggʷej aṭṭas di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI nwem. Minzi neccin nesřa xas řexbar u x marra min igga di Miṣra,
\v 10 d marra min igga Netta ak-d ijeǧiden n ayt n Imuriyyen inni yeǧan aɣirin i L’Urdun, Siḥun, ajeǧid n Ḥacbun, d Ɛuj, ajeǧid n Bacan nni tuɣa izeddeɣ di Ɛactarut. \x ◘ \xo 9:10 \xt Řxř. 21:24, 33; Aɛwd. 1:4\x*
\v 11 Uca ssiwřen akidneɣ imɣaren nneɣ d marra imezdaɣ n temmurt, nnan: ‘Ṭṭfem řeɛweč deg ufus nwem i webrid, uyurem i umsagar akidsen uca ad asen tinim: Neccin d imsexxaren nwem.’ Xenni řexxu, ggem akidneɣ ijj n řɛahd.
\v 12 Aɣrum-a nneɣ da tuɣa ɛad iḥma umi t-i-dd akidneɣ neksi zi tudrin nneɣ d řeɛweč deg wass ařami ɣarwem dd-neṭṭef abrid. Řexxu aqa-t yuẓeɣ idweř ittfruruy.
\v 13 Uřa d tixuncay n yiřem n binu nni neccur, tuɣa atent n jdid, maca xzarem, řexxu feǧqent. Aqa \add d\add* arruḍ nneɣ d sandaliyat nneɣ ḥfant s webrid i iggʷejen s waṭṭas.”
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* ksin iryazen n Israil zi řeɛweč. War ksin ccwar zeg uqemmum n SIDI.
\v 15 Igga Yacuwa akidsen řehna u igga akidsen \add ɛawed\add* ijj n řɛahd, ad ten yejj ad ddaren uca uřa d řḥukkam n tmesmunt jjuǧen asen.
\b
\m 
\v 16 Awarni třata n wussan awarni i umi tuɣa i d asen wcin řɛahd, sřan nitni belli aqa d jjiran nsen, u aqa zeddɣen di řwesṭ nsen.
\v 17 \add Minzi\add* ayt n Israil kksen \add iqiḍan nsen\add* uca iwḍen ɣar tneddam nsen deg wass wiss třata. Tuɣa tineddam nsen Jibɛun d Kafira d Biɛrut d Qaryat-Yaɛarim.
\v 18 Ayt n Israil war ten nɣin ca, minzi řḥukkam n tmesmunt tuɣa jjuǧen asen \add aya\add* ɣar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil. S uyenni i teqqim marra tmesmunt tmuɣmuɣ x řḥukkam.
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* nnan marra řḥukkam n tmesmunt: “Neccin nejjuǧ asen \add aya\add* ɣar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil. S uyenni řexxu war nzemmar ad ten nḥada.
\v 20 Ittxeṣṣa ad nkemmeř \add tajaǧit-a\add* u ad ten nejj ad ddaren, maḥend war xaneɣ dd-iweṭṭi uduqqez n weɣḍab di ssibbet n tjaǧit nni d asen negga.
\v 21 Řḥukkam nnan asen: “Nitni ad qqimen ddaren uca ad dewřen d inezdamen d inuyam i marra tamesmunt, am mammec d asen t nnan řḥukkam.”
\m 
\v 22 Iřaɣa i-ten Yacuwa, inna: “Mayemmi xaneɣ tcemtem, tennam: ‘Neccin nzeddeɣ ɣar řaggʷaj s waṭṭas xawem!’, waxxa kenniw tzeddɣem di řwest n temmurt nneɣ?
\v 23 Řexxu xenni, kenniw tᵉttwaneɛřem. War zzaywem ittwakkes ad tiřim d imsexxaren, inezdamen d inuyam i Taddart n AREBBI inu.” \f ◼ \fr 9:23 \fk War zzaywem ittwakkes ad tiřim ....\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘War zzaywem ittwaqeṣṣ ...’.\f*
\v 24 Nitni arrin-dd x Yacuwa, nnan: “I imsexxaren nnec ittwanna nican belli SIDI, AREBBI nwem, yumur amsexxar nnes Musa, aqa Netta ad awem iwca marra tammurt uca ad ihellek marra imezdaɣ n temmurt zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem. \add S uya\add* tuɣa neggʷed aṭṭas x tudart nneɣ zzat i wudem nwem. S uyenni i negga neccin aya. \f ◼ \fr 9:24 \fk x tudart nneɣ\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘x řeɛmur nneɣ’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 9:24 \xt Aɛwd. 7:1, 2\x*
\v 25 Řexxu \add xenni\add*, xzar, aqa aneɣ deg ufus nnec. Egg akidneɣ min tᵉttwařid mliḥ d min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin nnec ḥima ad zzayneɣ tegged.”
\v 26 Ammu i zzaysen igga uca netta ifekk i-ten zeg ufus n ayt n Israil, ařami nitni war ten nɣin ca.
\v 27 Deg wass nni simant nnes igga i-ten Yacuwa d inezdamen d inuyam i tmesmunt u i uɛalṭar n SIDI, ař ass-a, deg wemcan nni ɣa yixḍar Netta.
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Amenɣi ɣar Jibɛun
\m 
\v 1 Imsar, umi Aduni-Ṣadaq, ajeǧid n Urcalim isřa, aqa Yacuwa tuɣa iṭṭef Ɛay, iḥarrem i-tt qaɛ uca aqa igga ak-d Ɛay d ajeǧid nnes am tuɣa igga ak-d Ariḥa u ak-d ujeǧid nnes u aqa imezdaɣ n Jibɛun ggin řehna ak-d ayt n Israil u zeddɣen di řwesṭ nsen, \x ◘ \xo 10:1 \xt Yac. 6:15; 9:15\x*
\v 2 \add aqa\add* nitni ggʷeden aṭṭas, minzi Jibɛun tuɣa d ict n tendint temɣar, umi tt tuɣa am yicten zi \add jar\add* tneddam n tgeldit. Tuɣa-tt temɣar x Ɛay u marra iryazen nnes tuɣa aten d ayt n bu-teɣruḍt.
\v 3 Issekk Aduni-Zedek, ajeǧid n Urcalim, \add imsekkan\add* ɣar Huham, ajeǧid n Ḥabrun, ɣar Fir’am, ajeǧid n Yarmut, ɣar Yafiɛ, ajeǧid n Laxic u ɣar Dabir, ajeǧid n Ɛajlun, inna:
\v 4 “Geɛɛdem-dd ɣari u tewcem ayi afus. Ejj aneɣ ad newwet Jibɛun, minzi tegga řehna ak-d Yacuwa u ak-d ayt n Israil.”
\v 5 Nitni munen uca geɛɛden xemsa n ijeǧiden n Imuriyyen: ajeǧid n Urcalim, ajeǧid n Ḥabrun, ajeǧid n Yarmut, ajeǧid n Ɛajlun, nitni d marra řɛeskar nsen uca nnḍen i Jibɛun uca kkaren mmenɣen akides.
\m 
\v 6 Ssekken iryazen n Jibɛun \add ireqqasen\add* i Yacuwa, ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar di Jiljal, nnan: “War semmeḥ ifassen nnec deg imsexxaren nnec, as-dd deɣya ɣarneɣ. Senjem aneɣ d tewced aneɣ afus, minzi marra ijeǧiden n ayt n Imuriyyen, inni i izeddɣen deg idurar, aqa munen xaneɣ.”
\m 
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* igeɛɛed-dd Yacuwa zi Jiljal, netta d marra řgens n řɛeskar akides d marra ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen.
\v 8 \add Minzi\add* SIDI inna i Yacuwa “War tteggʷed ca zzaysen, minzi wciɣ ten deg ufus nnec. Uřa d ijj zzaysen war izemmar ad ibedd zzat i wudem nnec.”
\v 9 Yacuwa ihwa-dd xasen s řɣefřet. Igeɛɛaden-dd zi Jiljal ǧiřet am tekmeř.
\v 10 SIDI issnexřeɛ i-ten zzat i wudem n Israil uca igga asen ijj n weɣḍar d ameqqran ɣar Jibɛun uca netta iḍfar i-ten x webrid ittgeɛɛaden ɣar Bayt-Ḥurun uca iwwet i-ten ař ṭṭarf n Ɛaziqqa d Maqida.
\v 11 Imsar umi nitni arewřen zzat i wudem n Israil deg uhekkwu ɣar Bayt-Ḥurun, aqa SIDI inḍar xasen iẓra d imeqqranen zeg ujenna ař Ɛaziqqa uca mmuten. Inni immuten s ibquqen n tebruri tuɣa aten ktar zeg inni ittwanɣen s ssif s ifassen n ayt n Israil.
\m 
\v 12 Xenni issiweř Yacuwa ak-d SIDI, deg wass umi isellem SIDI Imuriyyen i ayt n Israil, inna zzat i tiṭṭawin n Israiliyyen: “\add A\add* tafuct, bedd ɣar Jibɛun, i \add cek a,\add* ayur, ɣar teɣzurt n Ayalun”
\v 13 Uca tafuct tbedd d uyur iqqim ibedd ařami yuɣa řgens tasɣart x řɛedyan nnes. Ma war yura man aya deg wedlis ittwannḍen n umsegged? Tafuct tbedd di řwesṭ n ujenna u war tqeǧeq ad tɣeǧi, ɛřayen ijj n wass ikmeř.
\v 14 War din iǧi uřa d ijj n wass am wanita, \add war imsar\add* zic uřa awarni as, ijj n wass i di tuɣa isřa SIDI ɣar tmijja n ijj n weryaz ammu, minzi SIDI tuɣa immneɣ di ṭṭweɛ n Israil.
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* iɛqeb-dd Yacuwa d marra Israil akides, ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar di Jiljal.
\b
\m 
\v 16 Xemsa n ijeǧiden nni arewřen uca nnufaren deg ifri ɣar Maqqida.
\v 17 Ittwanna man aya i Yacuwa, nnan: “Aqa ttwafen xemsa n ijeǧiden. Nitni nnuffaren deg ifri ɣar Maqqida.
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* inna Yacuwa: “Seqnunniyem tiṣuḍar d timeqqranin x uqemmum n ifri uca ssbeddem iryazen xasen, ḥima ad xasen ɛessen.
\v 19 Kenniw \add s yixef nwem\add*, war tᵉttɣimam tbeddem. Ḍfarem řɛedyan nwem, wtem aɣezdis aneggaru nsen. War ten ttejjim ad adfen ɣar tneddam nsen, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem, igga awem ten deg ufus nwem.”
\v 20 Umi ikemmeř i-ten Yacuwa d ayt n Israil s ict n tecti tameqqrant ařami ttwaqḍan nitni, uca iwḍen \add mɣir\add* inni yarewřen ɣar tneddam ifaryen,
\v 21 aqa yareggʷeḥ marra řgens di řehna ɣar Yacuwa di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar ɣar Maqqida. Uřa d ijj \add war izɛim\add* ad issenhez iřes nnes x ayt n Israil.
\m 
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* inna Yacuwa: “Arzmem aqemmum n ifri uca awyem-dd xemsa n ijeǧiden nni zeg ifri ɣari da!”
\v 23 Nitni ggin \add t\add* ammu, ssuffɣen-dd xemsa n ijeǧiden zeg ifri ɣares: ajeǧid n Urcalim, ajeǧid n Ḥabrun, ajeǧid n Yarmut, ajeǧid n Laxic d ujeǧid n Ɛajlun.
\v 24 Umi dd-ssuffɣen nitni ijeǧiden nni ɣar Yacuwa, iřaɣa Yacuwa marra iryazen n Israil uca inna i ikumandaren x iɛeskariyyen nni tuɣa akides iruḥen: “Qarrbem-dd uca sarsem iḍaren nwem x tmejjarin n ijeǧiden-a.” Qarrben-dd nitni uca ssarsen iḍaren x timejjarin nsen.
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* inna asen Yacuwa: “War tteggʷdem ca, war ttejjim ad iɛqez wuř nwem, iřim d iryazen u iřim tmeḥḍem, minzi ammu i ɣa igg SIDI ak-d marra řɛedyan nwem, inni ak-d tᵉttmenɣam.”
\v 26 Xenni iwwet i-ten Yacuwa uca inɣa i-ten. Yayeř i-ten ɣar xemsa n tḥenya uca qqimen ayřen ɣar tḥenya ařami d tameddit. \x ◘ \xo 10:26 \xt Aɛwd. 21:23; Yac. 8:29\x*
\v 27 Imsar ɣar řweqt n uɣeǧay n tfuct, issekk Yacuwa maḥend ad ten-i-dd-kksen zi tḥenya, ad ten nḍaren deg ifri i di tuɣa nnuffaren. Xenni ggin tiṣuḍar d timeqqranin x uqemmum n ifri, \add inni din iǧan\add* ař ass-a.
\v 28 Deg wass nni iṭṭef Yacuwa \bd Maqqida\bd* uca iwwet i-tt s řeqḍeɛ n ssif. Uca ajeǧid nnes, iḥarrem i-t uřa d \add marra\add* nitni d kuř řeɛmar nni \add iǧan\add* deg wemcan nni. War ijji ad iqqim uřa d ijj n umarweř uca igga ak-d ujeǧid n Maqqida am mammec tuɣa igga ak-d ujeǧid n Ariḥa.
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* iẓwa Yacuwa ak-d marra ayt n Israil zi Maqqida ɣar Libna uca immneɣ ak-d Libna.
\v 30 Uca SIDI iwca i-tt deg ufus n Israil, ak-d ujeǧid nnes. Iwwet i-tt s řeqḍeɛ n ssif ak-d marra řeɛmar i dayes \add iǧan\add*, war ijji ad iqqim uřa d ijj n umarweř, uca igga ak-d ujeǧid nnes am mammec tuɣa igga ak-d ujeǧid n Ariḥa.
\m 
\v 31 \add Xenni\add* iẓwa Yacuwa zi Libna ɣar \bd Laxic\bd* d marra Israil akides uca inneḍ as-dd i tendint uca immneɣ akides.
\v 32 SIDI iwca Laxic deg ufus n Israil. Uca Israil iṭṭef i-tt deg wass wiss tnayen uca iwwet i-tt s řeqḍeɛ n ssif ak-d marra řeɛmar i dayes \add iǧan\add*, ammu nican am mammec tuɣa i-tt igga ak-d Libna.
\v 33 Xenni igeɛɛed Huram, ajeǧid n Jazar, maḥend ad iɛawen Laxic, \add maca\add* Yacuwa iwwet i-t uřa d řgens nnes ařami war ijji ad ɣares iqqim uřa d ijj n umarweř.
\m 
\v 34 Yacuwa iẓwa zi Laxic ɣar \bd Ɛajlun\bd* d marra Israil akides uca nnḍen as-dd uca mmenɣen akides.
\v 35 Ṭṭfen tt deg wass nni uca wtin tt s řeqḍeɛ n ssif uca deg wass nni iḥarrem marra řeɛmar i dayes \add iǧan\add*, ammu nican am mammec tuɣa igga ak-d Laxic.
\m 
\v 36 Iẓwa Yacuwa zi Ɛajlun ɣar \bd Ḥabrun\bd* d marra Israil akides, uca mmenɣen akides.
\v 37 Nitni ṭṭfen tt uca wtin tt s řeqḍeɛ n ssif, ajeǧid nnes d marra tineddam nnes ak-d marra řeɛmar i dayes \add iǧan\add*. War ijji ad iqqim uřa d ijj n umarweř, ammu nican am mammec tuɣa igga ak-d Ɛajlun. Netta iḥarrem i-tt ak-d marra řeɛmar i dayes \add iǧan\add*.
\m 
\v 38 Uca idweř-dd Yacuwa ɣar \bd Dabir\bd* d marra Israil akides uca immneɣ akides.
\v 39 Netta iṭṭef i-tt u nitni wtin ajeǧid nnes d marra tineddam nnes s řeqḍeɛ n ssif uca ḥarrmen marra řeɛmar i dayes \add iǧan\add*. Netta war ijji ad iqqim uřa d ijj n umarweř. Am mammec tuɣa igga netta ak-d Ḥabrun, ammu igga \add ɛawed\add* ak-d Dabir u ak-d ujeǧid nnes igga am tuɣa igga ak-d ujeǧid n Libna.
\v 40 \add Ammu\add* i iɣřeb Yacuwa x marra tammurt: Tammurt n Idurar d \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub d Temmurt Iwaṭan, d marra ijeǧiden nsen. War ijji ad iqqim uřa d ijj n umarweř. Marra min tuɣa ittarran nnefs, iḥarrem i-t i uteḥḥi, am mammec tuɣa i d as yumur SIDI AREBBI n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 10:40 \xt Aɛwd. 7:2; 20:16, 17; Yac. 8:2\x*
\v 41 Yacuwa iwwet i-ten zi Qadac-Barniɛ ař Ɣazza u ammu uřa d marra tammurt n Jucan, ař Jibɛun.
\v 42 Iṭṭef Yacuwa ijeǧiden-a d temmurt nsen s ict n tecti, minzi SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, immneɣ di ṭṭweɛ n Israil.
\v 43 \add Xenni\add* iɛqeb Yacuwa ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar di Jiljal d marra Israil akides.
\b
\b
\c 11
\s1 Amenɣi ḍidd i ujeǧid Yabin d ijeǧiden nni akis iǧan
\m 
\v 1 Umi Yabin, ajeǧid n \bd Ḥaṣur\bd*, isřa aya, issekk ɣar Yubab, ajeǧid n \bd Madun\bd*, ɣar ujeǧid n \bd Cimrun\bd*, ɣar ujeǧid n \bd Akcaf\bd*,
\v 2 u ɣar ijeǧiden inni tuɣa \add izeddɣen\add* ɣar ccamal di Temmurt n Idurar u di Řewḍa ɣar ljanub zi Kinnarut u di Temmurt Iwaṭan u x tiwririn n Dur ɣar řɣarb,
\v 3 ɣar ayt n Kenɛan di ccarq d řɣarb, Imuriyyen, Iḥittiyyen, Ifiriziyyen, Iyabusiyyen deg idurar d Iḥiwiyyen ɣar uḍar n \add wedrar\add* n Hirmun, di temmurt n Miṣfa.
\v 4 Ffɣen-dd nitni s marra řɛeskar nsen akidsen, ijj n ubarra ameqqran n řgens, am yijdi ɣar tma n řebḥar, anect aṭṭas, uca \add arni ɣares\add* aṭṭas s waṭṭas n iysan d ikarruten.
\v 5 Marra ijeǧiden-a řaɣan-dd xasen uca usin-dd, wtin iqiḍan nsen jmiɛ ɣar waman n Mayrum i umenɣi ḍidd i Israil.*
\b
\m 
\v 6 Inna SIDI i Yacuwa: “War zzaysen tteggʷed, minzi tiwecca ɣar řweqt ammu řexxu ad ten ggeɣ ttwaɣeřben marra zzat i wudem n Israil. Cek ad tqessed iẓewran n iḍaren n iysan nsen uca ad tesscemḍed ikarruten nsen di tmessi.”
\m 
\v 7 Yacuwa s marra řɛeskar akides, iffeɣ-dd ɣarsen s ict n řɣefřet ɣar waman n Mayrum uca wḍan-dd xasen.
\v 8 SIDI igga i-ten deg ufus n Israil uca nitni wtin ten, ḍfaren ten ař Ṣidun-Ameqqran d Misrafut-Mayim, u ař taysart n Miṣfa ɣar ccarq. Nitni qḍan ten ařami war zzaysen jjin ad iqqim uřa d ijj n umarweř.
\v 9 Yacuwa igga akidsen am mammec d as inna SIDI. Netta iqess iẓewran n iḍaren n iysan nsen uca issecmeḍ ikarruten nsen s tmessi.
\m 
\v 10 Di řweqt nni iɛqeb Yacuwa uca iṭṭef Ḥaṣur uca iwta ajeǧid nnes s \add řeqḍeɛ n\add* ssif, minzi Ḥaṣur tuɣa-t qbeř d azeǧif x marra tigeldiwin-a.
\v 11 Wtin marra řeɛmar \add iddaren\add* nni dayes iǧan s řeqḍeɛ n ssif uca ḥarrmen ten u nɣin ten. War iqqim walu zi marra min ittarran nnefs uca issecmeḍ Ḥaṣur s tmessi.
\v 12 Iṭṭef Yacuwa marra tineddam n ijeǧiden-a s marra ijeǧiden nsen uca iwta i-ten s řeqḍeɛ n ssif uca iḥarrem i-ten, am mammec tuɣa yumur Musa, amsexxar n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 11:12 \xt Aɛwd. 20:16, 17; Yac. 10:40\x*
\v 13 Marra tineddam nni ibedden x tiwririn war tent sscemḍen Israiliyyen s tmessi, mɣir Ḥaṣur umi issecmeḍ Yacuwa s tmessi.
\v 14 Keccḍen ayt n Israil marra takeccaḍt n tneddam d řebhayem i ixef nsen. Maca nitni nɣin marra iwdan s řeqḍeɛ n ssif, ařami ten teḥḥan. Marra min ittaran nnefs, war zzayes jjin uřa d ijj.
\b
\s1 Lista n marra min iṭṭef Yacuwa n temmurt n Kenɛan
\m 
\v 15 Am mammec \add t\add* yumur SIDI i umsexxar nnes Musa, ammu i t igga Musa x Yacuwa, uca ammu \add i-t\add* igga Yacuwa. Netta war ismiḥ uřa deg ijj n wawař zi marra \add awařen\add* i yumur SIDI i Musa \add maḥend ad t igg\add*. \x ◘ \xo 11:15 \xt Uf. 23:32, 33; 34:12; Řxř. 33:52; Aɛwd. 7:2; 20:16\x*
\v 16 \add Ammu\add* iṭṭef Yacuwa marra tammurt nni: Tammurt n Idurar d marra \add Tammurt n\add* Ljanub d marra tammurt n Jucan d Temmurt Iwaṭan d Řewḍa d idurar n Israil d řwaṭa nnes,
\v 17 \add marra tammurt\add* zeg Wedrar d Aqeccar, wenni isgeɛɛaden ɣar Saɛir ař Baɛl-Jad, di teysart n Lubnan, swadday i wedrar n Ḥirmun. Marra ijeǧiden nsen iḥebbes i-ten, iwta i-ten uca inɣa i-ten.
\v 18 Aṭṭas n wussan i immneɣ Yacuwa ak-d marra ijeǧiden-a.
\v 19 War iǧi uřa d ict n tendint i iggin řehna ak-d ayt n Israil, mɣir Iḥiwiyyen, inni tuɣa izeddɣen di Jibɛun. Nitni ṭṭfen tent marra s umenɣi.
\v 20 Minzi SIDI tuɣa igga ad isseqseḥ uř nsen ař dd ɣa ffɣen ad mmenɣen ak-d Israil, ḥima ad ten iḥarrem uca war xasen yareḥḥem, ḥima ad ten iqḍa, am mammec tuɣa yumur SIDI i Musa.
\m 
\v 21 Di řweqt nni iffeɣ Yacuwa uca iteḥḥa \bd Iɛanaqiyyen\bd* zi temmurt n idurar, zi Ḥabrun, zi Dabir, zi Ɛanab, zi marra Tammurt n Idurar n Yahuda u zi marra tammurt n idurar n Israil. Yacuwa iḥarrem i-ten ak-d tneddam nsen i uteḥḥi.
\v 22 Di temmurt n ayt Israil war qqimen ɛad Iɛanaqiyyen. Qqimen mɣir di Ɣazza, Jat d Acdud.
\m 
\v 23 Iṭṭef Yacuwa marra tammurt nni, am mammec marra i tuɣa issiweř SIDI ɣar Musa, uca Yacuwa iwca i-tt d řwart i Israil ɛlaḥsab tirbiɛin n tqebbař nsen. \add Xenni\add* tuɣa tammurt tareyyeḥ zeg umenɣi.
\b
\b
\c 12
\s1 Aɣřeb x waḥd u třatin n ijeǧiden
\m 
\v 1 Ina d ijeǧiden n temmurt, inni x ɣeřben ayt n Israil uca \add xenni\add* ṭṭfen nitni tammurt nsen d řwart, aɣirin i L’Urdun zi manis i d tneqqar tfuct, zi teɣzart n Arnun ař idurar n Ḥirmun d marra Řewḍa di ccarq.
\m 
\v 2 Ɣar umezwaru nsen, Siḥun, ajeǧid n Imuriyyen, wenni tuɣa izeddɣen di Ḥacbun, netta iḥkem \add x jjwayeh\add* zi Ɛaruɛir i iǧan ɣar tma n teɣzart n Arnun, \add ař\add* řwesṭ n teɣzart, u x wezyen n Jilɛad ař tiɣzart n Yabbuq, \add aqa-t\add* d aymir n ayt n Ɛammun,
\v 3 u x Řewḍa ař řebḥar n Kinnarut di ccarq u ař řebḥar n Řewḍa, Řebḥar Ameǧaḥ, di ccarq, abrid n Bayt-Yacimut, u zi ljanub ař swadday i teysarin n Fisja.
\m 
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* tammurt n Ɛuj, ajeǧid n Bacan, \add wenni iǧan\add* zi min iqqimen zeg Irafawiyyen, \add jwaheř\add* i tuɣa izeddɣen di Ɛactarut d Idraɛi. \x ◘ \xo 12:4 \xt Aɛwd. 1:4\x*
\v 5 Netta iḥkem x idurar n Ḥirmun, x Salxa u x marra Bacan ař weymir n Ijacuriyyen d Imaɛkiyyen u x wezyen n Jilɛad ař tammurt n Siḥun, ajeǧid n Ḥacbun.
\m 
\v 6 Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, ak-d ayt n Israil, wtin ten u Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, tuɣa iwca \add tammurt nni\add* d řwart i Irubiniyyen d Ijadiyyen u i wezyen n teqbič n Manassa. \x ◘ \xo 12:6 \xt Řxř. 21:24; 32:33\x*
\b
\m 
\v 7 Ina d ijeǧiden n temmurt inni x iɣřeb Yacuwa d ayt n Israil, ɣar ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun di lɣarb, zi Baɛl-Jad di teysart n Lubnan ař adrar aqeccar wenni issgeɛɛden ɣar Saɛir. Uca Yacuwa iwca i-tt d řwart i tqebbař n Israil ɛlaḥsab tirbiɛin nsen, \x ◘ \xo 12:7 \xt Yac. 10:40\x*
\v 8 Di Temmurt n Idurar u di Temmurt Iwaṭan u di Řewḍa u di teysarin u di řexřa u di \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub: Iḥittiyyen, Imuriyyen, ayt n Kenɛan, Ifariziyyen, Iḥiwiyyen d Iyabusiyyen.
\b
\m 
\v 9 Ajeǧid n Ariḥa: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Ɛay \add i iǧan\add* ɣar uɣezdis n Bayt-Il: d ijj.
\m 
\v 10 Ajeǧid n Urcalim: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Ḥabrun: d ijj.
\m 
\v 11 Ajeǧid n Yarmut: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Laxic: d ijj.
\m 
\v 12 Ajeǧid n Ɛajlun: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Jazar: d ijj.
\m 
\v 13 Ajeǧid n Dabir: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Jadar: d ijj.
\m 
\v 14 Ajeǧid n Ḥurma: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Ɛarad: d ijj.
\m 
\v 15 Ajeǧid n Libna: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Ɛadullam: d ijj.
\m 
\v 16 Ajeǧid n Maqqida: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Bayt-Il: d ijj.
\m 
\v 17 Ajeǧid n Taffuḥ: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Ḥafar: d ijj.
\m 
\v 18 Ajeǧid n Afiq: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Laccarun: d ijj.
\m 
\v 19 Ajeǧid n Madun: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Ḥaṣur: d ijj.
\m 
\v 20 Ajeǧid n Cimrun-Mara’un: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Akcaf: d ijj.
\m 
\v 21 Ajeǧid n Taɛnak: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Majiddu: d ijj.
\m 
\v 22 Ajeǧid n Qadac: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Yuqnaɛam ɣar Karmal: d ijj.
\m 
\v 23 Ajeǧid n Dur x tiwririn ɣar Dur: d ijj.
\m Ajeǧid n Juyim di Jiljal: d ijj.
\m 
\v 24 Ajeǧid n Tirṣa: d ijj.
\b
\m Marra ijeǧiden-a aqa aten di waḥit u-třatin.
\b
\b
\c 13
\s1 SIDI issiweř ak-d Yacuwa
\m 
\v 1 Umi tuɣa Yacuwa d awessar uca imɣar deg wussan \add n tudart nnes\add*, inna as SIDI: “Cek tewsared u temɣared deg wussan uca \add ɛad\add* teqqim aṭṭas n temmurt maḥend ad tt teksid d řwart.
\v 2 Ta d tammurt iqqimen: marra iduwwaren n Ifilisṭiniyyen u marra \add jjwayeh n\add* Ijacuriyyen,
\v 3 zeg \add yeɣzar n\add* Ciḥur nni \add issizzřen\add* zzat i wudem n Miṣra, ař aymir n Ɛiqrun di ccamal nni ittwaḥseb-dd \add d tammurt\add* n ayt n Kenɛan, \add dayes\add* xemsa n řbacat \add n tneddam\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen, \add ixs ad yini\add* Aɣazi d Acdudi d Acqaluni, Ajitti, d Aɛaqruni, d Iɛawiyyen,
\v 4 \add uca xenni\add* zi ljanub marra tammurt n ayt n Kenɛan d Muɣara tenni n Iṣiduniyyen, ař Afiq u ař weymir n Imuriyyen,
\v 5 uca \add xenni\add* tammurt n Ijibliyyen d marra Lubnan manis i dd-tneqqar tfuct, zi Baɛl-Jad swadday i wedrar n Ḥirmun ař mani ittakkwaḍ \add bnadem\add* ɣar Ḥamat,
\v 6 marra inni izeddɣen \add di jjwayeh\add* zeg idurar n Lubnan ař Misrafut-Mayim, marra Iṣiduniyyen. Necc ad xasen aẓẓřeɣ zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil. Egg \add maca\add* tammurt d řwart i Israil waha, am mammec d ac umureɣ.”
\b
\s1 Tasɣart n Rubin, n Jad u i wezyen n teqbič n Manassi
\m 
\v 7 “Bḍa řexxu tammurt-a d řwart jar tesɛa n tqebbař d wezyen n teqbič n Manassa,
\v 8 \add iryazen n Manassa\add* nni iksin ak-d Irubiniyyen d Ijadiyyen tasɣart n řwart nsen nni i d asen iwca Musa x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun di ccarq, am mammec d asen \add tt\add* iwca Musa, amsexxar n SIDI:
\v 9 zi Aruɛir \add i iǧan\add* x tma n Arnun d tendint i iǧan di řwesṭ n teɣzurt d marra řwaṭa \add yuɛřan\add* zi Miydaba ař Dibun, \x ◘ \xo 13:9 \xt Aɛwd. 2:36\x*
\v 10 d marra tineddam n Siḥun, ajeǧid n Imuriyyen wenni tuɣa iḥekkmen di Ḥacbun, ař aymir n ayt n Ɛammun
\v 11 uřa d Jilɛad d temmurt n Ijacuriyyen d Imaɛkiyyen d qaɛ wedrar n Ḥirmun d marra Bacan ař Salxa,
\v 12 marra tageldit n Ɛuj, di Bacan, wenni tuɣa iḥekkmen di Ɛactarut d Idraɛi. Netta tuɣa iqqim zi min iqqimen n Irafawiyyen nni tuɣa iwta i-ten Musa uca yuẓẓeř xasen \add zi tesɣart nsen\add*.
\v 13 \add Maca\add* ayt n Israil war uẓẓřen x ayt n Ijacuriyyen d Imaɛkiyyen \add zi tesɣart nsen\add*. Jacur d Maɛkat qqimen zeddɣen di řwesṭ n ayt n Israil ař ass-a.
\m 
\v 14 I teqbič n Lawi waha umi i war iwci tasɣart. Tiɣarṣa n tmessi n SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, d tasɣart nnes, am mammec tuɣa i d as issiweř Netta.
\b
\m 
\v 15 Iwca Musa i \bd teqbič n ayt n Rubin\bd* \add tasɣart nsen\add*, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\v 16 I nitni umi dd-tekkar temmurt n Aruɛir, tenni i iǧan ɣar tma n teɣzart n Arnun ak-d tendint nni \add iǧan\add* di řwesṭ n teɣzurt d marra řwaṭa \add yuɛřan\add* ař Midiba.
\v 17 Ḥacbun d marra tineddam nnes nni \add iǧan\add* x řwaṭa \add yuɛřan\add*: Dibun, Bamut-Baɛl d Bayt-Baɛl-Maɛun
\v 18 d Yahṣa d Qadimut d Mayfaɛa
\v 19 d Qaryatayim d Sibma d Ṣarat-Ha-Caḥar x wedrar n řewḍa n teɣzurt, \f ◼ \fr 13:19 \fk Qiryatayim\ft - ixs ad yini ‘tnayen n tneddam’.\f*
\v 20 d Bayt-Faɣur d tisawnin n Fisja d Bayt-Yacimut,
\v 21 marra tineddam x řwaṭa \add yuɛřan\add* d marra tageldit n Siḥun, ajeǧid n Imuriyyen, inni i tuɣa iḥekkmen di Ḥacbun, i x iɣřeb Musa, \add am iɣřeb\add* uřa x řḥukkam n Midyan: Awi d Raqam d Ṣur d Ḥur d Rabaɛ, inni i d asen iwca Ṣihun jjehd akides, imezdaɣ n temmurt.
\v 22 Sennej i marra inni ittwanɣen di garra, nɣin ayt n Israil ɛawed Balɛam, mmis n Baɛur, agezzan, s řeqḍeɛ n ssif. \x ◘ \xo 13:22 \xt Řxř. 31:8\x*
\v 23 Tuɣa L’Urdun ak-d jjwayeh nnes d aymir n ayt n Rubin ak-d temmurt ɣar tma nnes. Ta d tasɣart n ayt n Rubin ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, ak-d tneddam d dcurat nsen. \x ◘ \xo 13:23 \xt Řxř. 34:14, 15\x*
\m 
\v 24 Iwca Musa i \bd teqbič n Jad\bd*, i ayt n Jad, \add tasɣart nsen\add* ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\v 25 I nitni umi dd-tekkar temmurt n Yaɛazir d marra tineddam n Jilɛad d wezyen n temmurt n ayt n Ɛammun ař Aruɛir nni \add iǧan\add* zzat i wudem n Rabba,
\v 26 zi Ḥacbun ař Ramat-Miṣfa d Buṭunim, u zi Maḥanayim ař aymir n Dabir.
\v 27 U di řewḍa n teɣzurt: Bayt-Haram d Bayt-Nimra d Sukkut d Ṣafun d min iqqimen n tgeldit n Siḥun, ajeǧid n Ḥacbun, L’Urdun d jjwayeh nnes ař aneggar n řebḥar n Kinnarat x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun ɣar ccarq.
\v 28 Ta d tasɣart n ayt n Jad, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, tineddam d dcurat nnes.
\m 
\v 29 Iwca Musa i \bd wezyen n teqbič n Manassa\bd* \add tasɣart nsen\add*. Tekkar as-dd i wezyen n teqbič n Manassa, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\v 30 Tuɣa tammurt nsen zi Maḥanayim: marra Bacan, marra tageldit n Ɛuj, ajeǧid n Bacan, d marra dcurat n Ya’ir nni \add iǧan\add* di Bacan, settin n tneddam. \x ◘ \xo 13:30 \xt Řxř. 32:14, Aɛwd. 3:4, 14\x*
\v 31 D wezyen n Jilɛad d Ɛactarut d Idriɛi, tineddam n tgeldit n Ɛuj di Bacan, kkaren-dd i iḥenjiren n Maxir, mmis n Manassa, aqa i wezyen n iḥenjiren n Maxir, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\v 32 Tina d \add jjwayeh\add* i tuɣa ibḍa Musa d řwart di řewḍat n Mu’ab, x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, ɣar Ariḥa, ɣar ccarq.
\m 
\v 33 Maca i \bd teqbič n Lawi\bd* war d as iwci Musa ca tasɣart. SIDI, AREBBI n Israil d tasɣart nsen, am mammec tuɣa akidsen issiweř. \x ◘ \xo 13:33 \xt Řxř. 18:20; Aɛwd. 10:9; 18:2\x*  *
\b
\b
\c 14
\s1 Abeṭṭu n temmurt ɣar ujemmaḍ n yeɣzar n L’Urdun
\m 
\v 1 Tina d tseqqar i ṭṭfen ayt n Israil di temmurt n Kenɛan, tinni i d asen ibḍa \add d řwart\add* ukehhan Aliɛazar d Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, d izeǧifen \add n tudrin\add* n ibabaten n tqebbař n ayt n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 14:1 \xt Řxř. 34:17\x*
\v 2 S tqedduḥt \add ṭṭfen\add* marra tasɣart nsen, am mammec \add t\add* yumur SIDI s tsexxart n Musa zi jjihet n tesɛa n tqebbař d wezyen n teqbič. \x ◘ \xo 14:2 \xt Řxř. 26:55\x*
\v 3 Maɣar Musa tuɣa iwca i tnayen n tqebbař d wezyen n teqbič ict n tesɣart aɣirin i L’Urdun, \add maca\add* i Ilawiyyen war d asen iwci ca tasɣart di řwesṭ nsen.
\v 4 Aqa ayt n Yusuf ggin tnayen n tqebbař, Manassa d Ifrayim, u i Ilawiyyen war d as wcin ca tasɣart di temmurt maca \add mɣir\add* tineddam i tzeddiɣt d min iǧan zzatsent n ddmani n tarewsa i řebhayem u i min ɣarsen iǧan. \f ◼ \fr 14:4 \fk Ilawiyyen\ft - ixs ad yini ‘ayt n Lawi’.\f*
\v 5 Am mammec tuɣa yumur SIDI i Musa, ammu i ggin ayt n Israil řami bḍan tammurt.
\m 
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* qarrben-dd ayt n Yahuda ɣar Yacuwa di Jiljal. \bd Kalib\bd*, mmis n Yafunni, Aqinizi, inna as: “Cek tessned min xafi d xak inna SIDI i Musa, aryaz n AREBBI, di Qadac-Barniɛ. \x ◘ \xo 14:6 \xt Řxř. 14:24; Aɛwd. 1:36\x*
\v 7 Necc ggiɣ arebɛin n iseggʷusa, umi i dd ayi issekk Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, zi Qadac-Barniɛ maḥend ad bergageɣ tammurt u necc ɛeqbeɣ ɣares, xebbareɣ as am mammec \add t\add* tuɣa deg wuř inu.
\v 8 \add Waxxa amenni\add* aytma, inni i tuɣa akidi igeɛɛden, ssfessyen uř n řgens, \add maca\add* necc tuɣa řebda ḍeffareɣ SIDI, AREBBI inu. \x ◘ \xo 14:8 \xt Řxř. 14:24\x*
\v 9 Deg wass nni ijjuǧ Musa, inna: “\add Wayyaw,\add* mařa tammurt i di tessarsed aḍar nnec, war tᵉttiři i cek d iḥenjiren nnec d tasɣart i řebda, minzi tuɣa cek řebda tḍeffared SIDI, AREBBI inu!”
\m 
\v 10 Řexxu, xzar, SIDI ijja ayi ddareɣ, am mammec issiweř. Řexxu aqa xemsa u-rebɛin n iseggʷusa zeg wami issiweř SIDI ɣar Musa awař-a, umi Israil yuyur di řexřa. Uca řexxu, aqa da, am mammec tᵉttwařid, ɣari xemsa u-tmanyin n iseggʷusa.
\v 11 Necc ɛad meḥḍeɣ am mammec \add meḥḍeɣ\add* deg wass nni umi i d ayi dd-issekk Musa. Am mammec tuɣa jehhdeɣ deg wussan nni, ammu i jehhdeɣ ɛawed iḍa i umenɣi maḥend ad ffɣeɣ u ad areggʷḥeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 14:11 \xt Řxř. 27:17; Aɛwd. 31:2\x*
\v 12 Řexxu \add xenni\add*, ewc ayi \add tammurt-a n\add* idurar i x issiweř SIDI deg wass nni, maɣar cek tesřid simant nnec deg wass nni, aqa ayt n Iɛanaqiyyen aqa aten dinni uřa d tineddam mɣarent u faryent. Ad taɣ ad kidi yiři SIDI, ad awḍeɣ ad xasen aẓẓřeɣ am mammec inna SIDI.”
\m 
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* ibarek i-t Yacuwa uca iwca Ḥabrun d řwart i Kalib, mmis n Yafunni.
\v 14 X uya teǧa \add tendint n\add* Ḥabrun d řwart n Kalib, mmis n Yafunni, Aqinizi, ař ass-a, minzi netta tuɣa řebda iḍeffar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.
\v 15 Ḥabrun tuɣa qqaren as zic ‘tandint n Arbaɛ’. Tuɣa \add Arbaɛ\add* d aryaz d ameqqran deg ayt n Iɛanaqiyyen. Uca tammurt tuɣa dayes řhudnet zeg umenɣi. \f ◼ \fr 14:15 \fk tandint n Arbaɛ\ft - niɣ ‘Qaryat-Arbaɛ’.\f*
\b
\b
\c 15
\s1 Tasɣart n Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 \bd Taqedduḥt\bd* i ayt n \bd Yahuda\bd*, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, tekkar-asent ɣar weymir n Idum, řexřa n Ṣin, ɣar ljanub, \add ař\add* ljanub qaɛ.
\v 2 \bd Aymir n ljanub\bd* tuɣa-t i nitni zi manis iqeṭṭa Řebḥar Ameǧaḥ, zeg yiřes \add n uqemmum\add* \add n Řebḥar\add* i dd-itteffɣen ɣar ljanub, \x ◘ \xo 15:2 \xt Řxř. 34:4\x*
\v 3 uca iɛeddu \add xenni\add* ɣar ljanub n Tsunta n Tɣarḍmiwin uca iɛeddu ɣar Ṣin uca ittgeɛɛed zi ljanub n Qadac-Barniɛ, ittekk x Ḥaṣrun u ittgeɛɛad ɣar Addar uca idekkwař ɣar Qarqaɛ
\v 4 u \add xenni\add* ittekk x Ɛaṣmun u itteffeɣ ɣar Teɣzart n Miṣra uca ṭṭrufa n weymir \add ttakkwaḍen\add* ař řebḥar. Wa aqa d aymir n ljanub i kenniw.
\m 
\v 5 \bd Aymir n ccarq\bd* aqa-t d Řebḥar Ameǧaḥ ɣar qeṭṭu n L’Urdun u \bd aymir n ccamal\bd* zeg yiřes n Řebḥar, zi manis iqeṭṭa L’Urdun
\v 6 u \add ssenni\add* ittgeɛɛed weymir \add ɣar\add* Bayt-Ḥujla uca iɛeddu ɣar ccamal n Bayt-Ɛaraba u \add xenni\add* ittgeɛɛed ař weẓru n Buhan, mmis n Rubin,
\v 7 uca ittgeɛɛed weymir zi Dabir zi Teɣzurt n Axur u ittenneḍ ɣar ccamal ɣar Jiljal wenni \add iǧan\add* ajemmaḍ i webrid n uẓekkwu x idurar n Adummim i \add iǧan\add* ɣar ljanub n teɣzart u \add xenni\add* iɛeddu weymir ɣar waman n Ɛayn-Camc uca itteffeɣ ɣar Ɛayn-Rujal.
\v 8 \add Zi ssa\add* ittgeɛɛed weymir zi teɣzurt n mmis n Hinnum, ɣar uɣezdis n ljanub \add n wedrar n\add* n Uyabusi, aqa-t d Urcalim, u aymir yarenni ittgeɛɛed ɣar tqiccat n wedrar wenni iǧan ɣar řɣarb n teɣzurt n mmis n Hinnum tenni iǧan ɣar jjihet n ccamal n uneggaru n teɣzurt n Irafawiyyen.
\v 9 Zi tqiccat n wedrar immars weymir ɣar tařa n Neftuḥa u iɛeddu ɣar tneddam n idurar n Ifrun u \add xenni\add* immars weymir ɣar Baɛala, tenni d Qaryat-Yaɛarim.
\v 10 Zi Baɛala ittakkwaḍ weymir ɣar řɣarb ɣar idurar n Saɛir uca iɛeddu zi ccamal ɣar uɣezdis n wedrar n Yaɛarim, aqa-t d Kasalun, uca ihekkwa ɣar Bayt-Cams u ittekk x Timnah.
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* iɛeddu weymir ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal n Ɛaqrun. \add Xenni\add* immars weymir ɣar Cakrun u ittekk x uɣezdis n wedrar n Baɛla u itteffeɣ ɣar Yabniyil uca ṭṭrufa n weymir takkwaḍen ař řebḥar.
\m 
\v 12 \bd Aymir n řɣarb\bd* \add iɛeddu\add* ař Řebḥar Ameqqran d tma \add n řebḥar\add*. Wa d aymir n ayt n Yahuda zi marra iɣezdisen, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen. \x ◘ \xo 15:12 \xt Řxř. 34:6\x*
\m 
\v 13 \add Maca\add* \bd Kalib\bd*, mmis n Yafunni, iwca as ict n tesɣart di řwesṭ n ayt n Yahuda, ɛlaḥsab tawṣeyyet zeg uqemmum n SIDI i Yacuwa, \add aqa-tt\add* d tandint n Arbaɛ. \add Arbaɛ\add* tuɣa d babas n Ɛanaq, ixs ad yini Ḥabrun. \x ◘ \xo 15:13 \xt Yac. 14:15; Řqḍ. 1:20\x*
\v 14 Yuẓẓeř Kalib ssenni x třata n iḥenjiren n Ɛanaq: Cicay, Aximan u Talmay, \add inni\add* dd-ittwaxeřqen i Ɛanaq. \x ◘ \xo 15:14 \xt Řqḍ. 1:10\x*
\v 15 Ssenni igeɛɛed ɣar imezdaɣ n Dabir. Dabir tuɣa qqaren as zic: tandint n Sifr.
\v 16 Inna Kalib: “Man wen i ɣa iwten tandint n Sifr ad tt iṭṭef, ad as wceɣ yeǧi Axsa d tamɣart!”
\v 17 Ɛutniyil, mmis n Qanaz, umas n Kalib, iṭṭef i-tt u \add Kalib\add* iwca as yeǧis Axsa d tamɣart.
\v 18 Imsar umi nettat tusa-dd ɣar Ɛutniyil, tarra i-t ad ittar ijj n yeyyar x babas uca teḍra x weɣyuř \add nnes\add*. Kalib isseqsa tt: “Min cem yuɣin?” \f ◼ \fr 15:18 \fk babas\ft - ixs ad yini ‘babas n temɣart, Kalib.’\f*  \x ◘ \xo 15:18 \xt Řqḍ. 1:14\x*
\v 19 Nettat tarra: “Ewc ayi ict n lbaraka, maɣar cek tewcid ayi ict n temmurt tuẓeɣ, \add xenni\add* ewc ayi uřa d řɛunṣarat n waman!” Uca iwca as řɛunṣarat n nnej d řɛunṣarat n wadday.
\m 
\v 20 Ta d tasɣart n teqbič n ayt n Yahuda, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 21 \add Tina\add* tuɣa d \bd tineddam iggʷejen\bd* n teqbič n ayt n Yahuda, ɣar weymir ak-d Idum di Temmurt n Ljanub: Qabṣiyil d Ɛidar d Yajur
\v 22 d Qina d Dimuna d Ɛadada
\v 23 d Qadac d Ḥaṣur d Yitnan
\v 24 d Zif d Ṭalam d Baɛlut
\v 25 d Ḥaṣur-Xadata d tneddam \add n\add* Ḥaṣrun, ta d Ḥaṣur.
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* Amam d Camaɛ d Mulada
\v 27 d Ḥaṣa-Jadda d Ḥacmun d Bayt-Falaṭ
\v 28 d Ḥaṣar-Cuɛal d Bi’r-Sebɛa d Bizyutiya
\v 29 d Baɛla d Ɛayyim d Ɛazam,
\v 30 d Altulad d Kisil d Ḥurma
\v 31 d Ṣiqlaɣ d Madmanna d Sansanna
\v 32 d Labayut d Cilḥim d Ɛayn d Rimmun. Marra tineddam aqa atent di \bd tesɛa u-ɛicrin\bd* ak-d ředcur nsent.
\m 
\v 33 Di Temmurt Iwaṭan: Icta’ul d Ṣurɛa d Acna
\v 34 d Zanux d Ɛayn-Jannim d Taffuḥ d Ɛaynam,
\v 35 d Yarmut d Adullam d Suku d Aziqa
\v 36 d Caɛarayim d Ɛaditayim d Judayra d Judayratayim. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd arbeɛṭac\bd* n tneddam ak-d ředcur nsent.
\m 
\v 37 Ṣanan d Ḥadaca d Mijdal-Jad
\v 38 d Dilan d Miṣfa d Yaqtiyil
\v 39 d Laxic d Buṣqat d Ɛajlun
\v 40 d Kabbun d Laḥmas d Kitlic
\v 41 d Judayrut d Bayt-Dajun d Naɛama d Maqqada. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd seṭṭac\bd* n tneddam ak-d ředcur nsent.
\m 
\v 42 Libna d Ɛatir d Ɛacan
\v 43 d Yaftaḥ d Acna d Naṣib
\v 44 d Qaɛila d Aksib d Marica. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd tesɛa\bd* n tneddam ak-d ředcur nsent.
\m 
\v 45 Ɛaqrun ak-d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen d ředcur nnes.
\v 46 Zi Ɛaqrun ař rebḥar, marra min iǧan ɣar uɣezdis n Acdud ak-d ředcur nsen.
\v 47 Acdud ak-d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen d ředcur nnes, Ɣazza ak-d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen d ředcur nnes ař Taɣzart n Miṣra d Řebḥar Ameqqran ak-d \add temmurt n\add* tma \add n řebḥar\add*.
\m 
\v 48 Di Temmurt n Idurar: Camir d Yattir d Suku
\v 49 d Danna d tendint n Sanna, ta d Dabir,
\v 50 d Ɛanab d Actimu d Ɛanim
\v 51 d Jucan d Ḥulun d Jilu. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd ḥiṭac\bd* n tneddam ak-d ředcur nsent.
\m 
\v 52 Arab d Duma d Acɛan
\v 53 d Yanum d Bayt-Taffuḥ d Afiqa
\v 54 d Ḥumṭa d Qaryat-Arbaɛ, tenni d Ḥabrun, d Ṣaɛur. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd tesɛa\bd* n tneddam ak-d ředcur nsent.
\m 
\v 55 Maɛun d Karmal d Zif d Yuṭa
\v 56 d Yizraɛil d Yuqdaɛam d Zanuḥ
\v 57 d Qayin d Jibɛa d Timnah. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd ɛecra\bd* n tneddam ak-d ředcur nsent.
\m 
\v 58 Ḥalḥul d Bayt-Ṣur d Jadur
\v 59 d Maɛarat d Bayt-Ɛanut d Iltaqun. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd setta\bd* n tneddam ak-d ředcur nsent.
\m 
\v 60 Qaryat-Baɛl, aqa-t d Qaryat-Yiɛarim d Rabba. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd tnayen\bd* n tneddam ak-d ředcur nsent.
\v 61 Di řexřa Bayt-Ɛaraba d Middin d Sakaka
\v 62 d Nibcan d tendint n Umeǧaḥ d Ɛayn-Jadi. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd setta\bd* n tneddam ak-d ředcur nsent.
\m 
\v 63 \add Maca\add* ayt n Yahuda war zemmaren ad aẓẓřen x Iyabusiyyen inni d imezdaɣ n Urcalim. \add X uyenni\add* zeddɣen Iyabusiyyen \add ɛad\add* ak-d ayt n Yahuda di Urcalim ař ass-a.
\b
\b
\c 16
\s1 Tasɣart n ayt n Yusuf: Manassi d Ifrayim
\m 
\v 1 \bd Taqedduḥt\bd* i ayt n \bd Yusuf\bd* tekkar as-dd zi L’Urdun ɣar Ariḥa, \add uca aymir\add* ittekk x tma n ccarq n waman n Ariḥa, \add x\add* řexřa nni dd-ittgeɛɛaden zi Ariḥa x idurar n Bayt-Il.
\v 2 U zi Bayt-Il itteffeɣ ɣar Luz, ittekk x temmurt n ayt n Arkit ɣar Ɛaṭarut
\v 3 uca ihekkwa-dd ɣar řɣarb ɣar temmurt n Ifalaṭiyyen ař tammurt n Bayt-Ḥurun n wadday u ař Jazar u ṭṭrufa nnes ttakkwaḍen ař řebḥar.
\m 
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* ṭṭfen uřa d ayt n Yusuf, Manassa d Ifrayim, řwart nsen.
\v 5 Aymir n ayt n \bd Ifrayim\bd*, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, d wa. Aymir n tesɣart nsen ibedda ɣar ccarq n Ɛaṭarut-Adar \add uca iggur\add* ař Bayt-Ḥurun n nnej,
\v 6 uca iggur ɣar řɣarb ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal n Mikmata uca ittefriɣ weymir ɣar ccarq ɣar Ta’anat-Cilu u \add xenni\add* ittekk xas x uɣezdis nnes n ccarq ɣar Yanuḥa,
\v 7 u zi Yanuḥa ihekkwa ɣar Ɛaṭarut d Naɛarata uca ɛřayen ineḥḥed Ariḥa u \add xenni\add* itteffeɣ ɣar L’Urdun.
\v 8 Zi Taffuḥ iɛeddu weymir ɣar řɣarb ɣar tiɣzart n Qana uca ṭṭrufa nnes ttakkwaḍen ař řebḥar. Ta d tasɣart n teqbič n ayt n Ifrayim, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\m 
\v 9 \bd Tineddam\bd* i ittwaḥuzen i ayt n Ifrayim aqa atent di řwesṭ n tesɣart n Manassa, marra tineddam ak-d ředcur nsent.
\v 10 War uẓẓiřen ca x ayt n Kenɛan nni tuɣa izeddɣen di Jazar \add zi tesɣart nsen\add*. \add Ammu\add* zeddɣen Ikenɛaniyyen \add ɛad\add* di řwesṭ n ayt n Ifrayim ař ass-a. Tᵉttwagg xasen \add maca\add* ljizya n tsexxart.
\b
\b
\c 17
\m 
\v 1 Tuɣa din \add ɛawed\add* ict n \bd taqedduḥt\bd* i teqbič n \bd Manassa\bd*, minzi netta tuɣa d amenzu n Yusuf, tekkar as-dd i Makir, amenzu n Manassa, babas n \add temmurt n\add* Jilɛad, Jilɛad d Bacan, maɣar netta tuɣa d ijj n uɛeskari imeḥḍen. \x ◘ \xo 17:1 \xt Amz. 46:20\x*
\v 2 Tekkar asen-dd tqedduḥt i ayt iqqimen n Manassa ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, i ayt n Abiɛazar d ayt n Ḥalaq d ayt n Asriyil d ayt n Cakam d ayt n Ḥafar d ayt n Camidaɛ. Ina d ayt n Manassa, mmis n Yusuf, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\m 
\v 3 U Zeluḥfad, mmis n Ḥafar, mmis n Jilɛad, mmis n Makir, mmis n Manassa, war ɣares tuɣi ca iḥenjiren, maca tuɣa ɣares yessis. Ina d ismawen n yessis: Maḥla d Nuɛa, Ḥujla, Milka d Tirṣa. \x ◘ \xo 17:3 \xt Řxř. 26:33; 27:1\x*
\v 4 Nitenti qarrbent-i-dd zzat i wudem n ukehhan Aliɛazar u zzat i wudem n Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, u zzat i wudem n řḥukkam, nnant: “SIDI yumur Musa, ad aneɣ iwc tasɣart jar aytmatneɣ.” Uca iwca asent, ɛlaḥsab řumur n SIDI, ict n tasɣart jar wawmaten n babatsent. \x ◘ \xo 17:4 \xt Řxř. 27:7; 36:2\x*
\m 
\v 5 Ammu i iwḍan ifiřan \add n řeɛbar\add* ɛecra n twařawin i Manassa, břa tammurt n Jilɛad d Bacan i iǧan aɣirin n L’Urdun.
\v 6 Maɣar yessis n Manassa ṭṭfent tasɣart di řwesṭ n warrawen nnes u tammurt n Jilɛad tuɣa i warrawen n Manassa i iqqimen.
\m 
\v 7 Aymir n Manassa itteffeɣ zi Acir iɛeddu ɣar Mikmata i iǧan ajemmaḍ i Cakim u aymir itteffeɣ ɣar ufusi ɣar imezdaɣ n Ɛayn-Taffuḥ.
\v 8 Manassa ɣares tammurt n Taffuḥ, maca Taffuḥ \add simant nnes\add* \add nni\add* iǧan x weymir ak-d Manassa, tuɣa i ayt n Ifrayim.
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* ihekkwa weymir ɣar teɣzart n Qana ɣar ljanub n teɣzart. Tineddam n Ifrayim aqa-tent din jar tneddam n Manassa. Tammurt n Manassa teǧa ɣar tma n ccamal n iɣzar uca ṭṭrufa nnes ttakkwaḍen ař řebḥar.
\v 10 Ljanub aqa n Ifrayim, ccamal aqa n Manassa u řebḥar d aymir nnes. Di ccamal ttenḥadan x Acir u di ccarq x Issakar.
\v 11 Di Issakar u di Acir dewřen ina ɣar Manassa: Bayt-Can ak-d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen u Yablaɛam ak-d tneddam nnes d imezdaɣ n Dur ak-d tneddam nnes d imezdaɣ n Ɛayn-Dur ak-d tneddam nnes d imezdaɣ n Taɛnak ak-d tneddam nnes d imezdaɣ n Majiddu ak-d tneddam nnes, třata n treqqiɛin uyřent.
\v 12 Ayt n Manassa war zemmaren ad \add zzaysen\add* ṭṭfen tineddam-a \add d tesɣart n řwart\add*, minzi ayt n Kenɛan ggin \add ad qqimen\add* zeddɣen di temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 17:12 \xt Řqḍ. 1:27\x*
\v 13 Umi ayt n Israil dewřen jehden, ggin nitni ljizya x ayt n Kenɛan, \add maca\add* war xasen uẓẓřen qaɛ.
\v 14 Ssiwřen ayt n Yusuf ak-d Yacuwa, nnan: “Mayemmi d ayi tewcid d tasɣart mɣir ict n tqedduḥt d yijj n ufiřu \add n řeɛbar\add*, waxxa necc d ijj n řgens d ameqqran, awarni i umi d ayi igga SIDI lbaraka ammu?”
\v 15 Yacuwa inna asen: “Mařa cek \add xenni\add* d ijj n řgens ameqqran, geɛɛed \add xenni\add* ɣar wezɣar uca zdem dinni ttasiɛ i yixef nnec di temmurt n Ifiriziyyen d Irafawiyyen, mařa ḥṣaren xak idurar n Ifrayim.” \f ◼ \fr 17:15 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* nnan ayt n Yusuf: “Idurar nni war d aneɣ ttqiddin. Marra ayt n Kenɛan nni izeddɣen di temmurt n řewḍa n teɣzurt ɣarsen ikarruten n umenɣi n wuzzař, am yinni \add izeddɣen\add* di Bayt-Can ak-d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen u am yinni di řewḍa n teɣzurt n Yazraɛil.”
\v 17 Issiweř Yacuwa ak-d taddart n Yusuf, ak-d Ifrayim d Manassa, inna: “Kenniw d ijj n řgens d ameqqran u ɣarwem jjehd ameqqran. Kenniw war tᵉttᵉṭṭfem mɣir ict n tqedduḥt,
\v 18 maɣar uřa d idurar ad iřin nwem uca umi \add teǧa\add* d azɣar, ittxeṣṣa ad tzedmem uca ṭṭrufa nnes ad iřin i kenniw, maɣar ad taẓẓřem x ayt n Kenɛan \add zi tesɣart nsen\add*, waxxa ɣarsen ikarruten n umenɣi n wuzzař u waxxa nitni jehden.”
\b
\b
\c 18
\s1 Tazeddiɣt d wagraw n řgens di Cilu
\m 
\v 1 Marra tamesmunt n ayt n Israil tmun di Cilu uca dinni i wtin Aqiḍun n Umsagar, \add awarni\add* umi sswaḍɛen tammurt i yixef nsen.
\v 2 Tuɣa qqiment jar ayt n Israil sebɛa n tqebbař, tinni tuɣa war d asent immewcen \add ɛad\add* d tasɣart nsent.
\m 
\v 3 Inna Yacuwa i ayt n Israil: “Ař meřmi ttrajam \add ɛad\add* ař ɣa tadfem ad tᵉṭṭfem tammurt i d awem iwca SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nwem, \add d řwart\add*?
\v 4 Ksim i yixef nwem třata n yeryazen zi kuř taqbič, ḥima necc ad ten ssekkeɣ uca nitni ad kkaren ad kken x temmurt uca ad tt zemmen zi jjihet mammec ittxeṣṣa ad tiři tesɣart nsen, \add xenni\add* ad ɣari dd-ɛeqben.
\v 5 Ad tt bḍan x sebɛa n tseqqar. Yahuda ad iqqim x temmurt nnes di ljanub u taddart n Yusuf ad teqqim x temmurt nnes di ccamal.
\v 6 Kenniw ad tzemmem tammurt x sebɛa n tseqqar uca izemmanen nni ad ayi ten dd-tawyem danita, \add xenni\add* necc ad awem nḍareɣ taqedduḥt zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ.
\v 7 Minzi Ilawiyyen war ɣarsen bu tasɣart di řwest nwem, minzi tukehhant n SIDI d tasɣart nsen. Jad d Rubin d wezyen n teqbič n Manassa ṭṭfen tasɣart nsen x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, ɣar ccarq, \add tasɣart\add* nni i d asen iwca Musa, amsexxar n SIDI.
\m 
\v 8 Kkaren iryazen uca ṭṭfen abrid. Yumur Yacuwa i yinni iṭṭfen abrid maḥend ad zemmen tammurt s tira, inna: “Uyurem, ttekkem x temmurt uca zemmemem tt. \add Xenni\add* ɛeqbettiw-dd ɣari u necc ad awem da nḍareɣ taqedduḥt di Cilu zzat i wudem n SIDI.”
\v 9 Iryazen ṭṭfen abrid, cuqen tammurt uca zemmen tt deg ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen, \add settfen tt\add* ɛlaḥsab tineddam, ɛlaḥsab sebɛa n tseqqar, uca ɛeqben ɣar Yacuwa di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar di Cilu.
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* inḍar Yacuwa taqedduḥt zzat i wudem n SIDI. Din i d asen ibḍa Yacuwa tammurt jar ayt n Israil, ɛlaḥsab tirbiɛin nsen.
\b
\s1 Tasɣart n Binyamin
\m 
\v 11 \bd Taqedduḥt\bd* n teqbič n \bd Binyamin\bd* teḍhar-dd ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, u tasɣart n tqedduḥt nsen tusa-dd jar ayt n Yahuda d ayt n Yusuf.
\m 
\v 12 Itteffeɣ weymir nsen ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal zi L’Urdun uca ittgeɛɛad ɣar weɛrur n ccamal n Ariḥa, iɛeddu \add xenni\add* ɣar řɣarb ittekk x idurar uca ṭṭrufa nnes ttakkwaḍen ař řexřa n Bayt-Awan. \x ◘ \xo 18:12 \xt Yac. 7:2\x*
\v 13 Ssenni iẓekkwa weymir ɣar Luz x weɛrur n ljanub n Luz, wa d Bayt-Il, uca \add xenni\add* ihekkwa-dd ɣar Ɛaṭarut x wedrar \add i iǧan\add* ɣar ljanub n Bayt-Ḥurun n wadday.
\m 
\v 14 Aymir iɛeddu uca ittmeyyeř jjihet n řɣarb, \add xenni\add* ɣar ljanub zeg wedrar \add i iǧan\add* arendad n Bayt-Ḥurun, \add xenni\add* yarenni iggur ɣar ljanub uca ṭṭrufa nnes ttakkwaḍen ař Qaryat-Baɛla, ta d Qaryat-Yaɛarim, ict n tendint n ayt n Yahuda. Wa d aɣezdis n řɣarb.
\m 
\v 15 Aɣezdis n ljanub \add itteffeɣ\add* zi ṭṭarf aneggar n Qaryat-Yaɛarim. Ibedda weymir zi řɣarb u ittakkwaḍ ɣar tařa n waman n Naftuḥa.
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* ihekkwa-dd weymir ɣar ṭṭarf n wedrar i zi tᵉttwařid taɣzurt n mmis n Hinnum nni iǧan ɣar ṭṭarf n ccamal n teɣzurt n Irafawiyyen uca \add xenni\add* ihekkwa-dd x teɣzurt n Hinnum ɣar uɣezdis n ljanub n \add wedrar n\add* Iyabusiyyen uca ihekkwa-dd ɣar tařa n Rujil.\x ◘ \xo 18:16 \xt Yac. 15:8, 7\x*
\v 17 Uca ittekk x ccamal uca ittakkwaḍ ɣar Ɛayn-Camc uca iɛeddu ɣar Jalilut, nni \add iǧan\add* arendad n webrid n uẓekkwu x idurar n Adummim uca ihekkwa-dd ɣar weẓru n Buhan, mmis n Rubin, \x ◘ \xo 18:17 \xt Yac. 15:6\x*
\v 18 u iẓekkwa ɣar řgeɛɛdet nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar ccamal arendad n Řewḍa uca \add xenni\add* ihekkwa di Řewḍa.
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* iɛeddu weymir ɣar ccamal ɣar řgeɛɛdet n Bayt-Ḥujla u ṭṭrufa nnes aqa aten ɣar iřes n ccamal n Řebḥar Ameǧaḥ, ɣar uneggar n L’Urdun di ljanub. Wa d aymir n ljanub.
\m 
\v 20 L’Urdun tuɣa d aymir nnes x uɣezdis n ccarq. Ta d tasɣart n ayt n Binyamin ɛlaḥsab iymiren nnes i d as iquwwaren, ɛlaḥasab řaǧat nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 21 Tineddam n teqbič n ayt n Binyamin, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen d tina: Ariḥa d Bayt-Ḥujla d Ɛimaq-Qiṣiṣ
\v 22 d Bayt-Ɛaraba d Ṣamarayim d Bayt-Il
\v 23 d Iɛawiyyen d Ha-Fara d Ɛufra,
\v 24 d Kafar-Ɛammuni d Ha-Ɛufni d Jabaɛ. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd tenɛac n tneddam\bd* ak-d ředcur nsent.
\m 
\v 25 Jibɛun d Rama d Biɛrut
\v 26 d Miṣfa d Kafira d Muṣa
\v 27 d Raqam d Yarafwil d Tarala
\v 28 d Ṣalaɛ d Alaf d Ayabusi, wenni d Urcalim, d Jibɛa d Qaryat. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd arbeɛṭac n tneddam\bd* ak-d ředcur nsent. Ta d tasɣart n ayt n Binyamin ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\b
\b
\c 19
\s1 X setta n tseqqar nneɣni
\m 
\v 1 \bd Taqedduḥt wiss tnayen\bd* tekkar as-dd i \bd Cimɛun\bd*, i teqbič n Cimɛun, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen. Tasɣart nsen teǧa di řwest n tesɣart n ayt n Yahuda.
\v 2 Di tesɣart nsen dewřent ɣarsen \add tneddam-a\add*: Bi’r-Sebɛa d Cabɛa d Mulada
\v 3 d Ḥaṣar-Cuɛal d Baɛla d Ɛaṣam
\v 4 d Iltulad d Batul d Ḥurma
\v 5 d Ṣiqlaɣ d Bayt-Markabut d Ḥaṣar-Susa
\v 6 d Bayt-Labawut d Caruḥayn. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd třeṭṭac n tneddam\bd* ak-d ředcur nsent.
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* Ɛayn d Rimmun d Ɛatar d Ɛacan. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd arebɛa n tneddam\bd* ak-d ředcur nsent,
\v 8 uřa d marra ředcur i dd-ittennḍen i tneddam-a ař Baɛlat-Bi’r, tenni d Rama n ljanub. Ta d tasɣart n teqbič n ayt n Cimɛun, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\m 
\v 9 Tasɣart n ayt n Cimɛun tuɣa \add tᵉttwaksi\add* zi \add min ɛebbaren s\add* ufiřu \add n řeɛbar\add* i ayt n Yahuda, minzi tasɣart n ayt n Yahuda tuɣa-tt i ina d tameqqrant aṭṭas. \add X uyenni\add* warten ayt n Cimɛun ict n tesɣart di tesɣart nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 10 \bd Taqedduḥt wiss třata\bd* teḍhar-dd i ayt n \bd Zabulun\bd*, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen. Aymir n tesɣart nsen iɛeddu ař Sarid.
\v 11 Ittgeɛɛed weymir nsen ɣar řɣarb u \add ɣar\add* Marɛala uca ittakkwaḍ ař Dabbaca u ař tiɣzart nni issizzřen zzat i Yuknaɛam.
\v 12 Zi Sarid ittmeyyeř weymir ɣar ccarq, ɣar manis d tneqqar tfuct, ař weymir n Kislut-Tabur uca itteffeɣ ɣar Dubra u ittgeɛɛed ɣar Yafiɛ.
\v 13 Ssenni iɛeddu ɣar ccarq, ɣar manis dd-tneqqar tfuct, ɣar Jat-Ḥafar u ɣar Ɛit-Qaṣin u itteffeɣ ɣar Rimmun, ittefriɣ \add xenni ɣar\add* Nayɛa.
\v 14 Ittefriɣ weymir zi ccamal ɣar Ḥannatun u ṭṭrufa nnes ttakkwaḍen ař teɣzurt n Jiftaḥ-Il.
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* Qaṭṭa d Nahlal d Cimrun d Yadala d Bayt-Laḥm. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd tenɛac n tneddam\bd* ak-d ředcur nsent.
\v 16 Ta d tasɣart n ayt n Zabulun, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, tineddam-a ak-d ředcur nsent.
\b
\m 
\v 17 \bd Taqedduḥt wiss arebɛa\bd* tekkar as-dd i \bd Issakar\bd*, i ayt n Issakar, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\v 18 Iɛeddu weymir nsen ɣar Yazraɛil d Kislut d Cunam
\v 19 d Ḥafarayim d Ciyun d Anaḥara
\v 20 d Rabbit d Qicyun d Abaṣ
\v 21 d Rama d Ɛayn-Jannim d Ɛayn-Ḥadda d Bayt-Qaṣṣays.
\v 22 Ittakkwaḍ weymir ař Tabur d Caḥṣima d Bayt-Cams u ṭṭrufa n weymir ttakkwaḍen ař L’Urdun. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd seṭṭac n tneddam\bd* ak-d ředcur nsent.
\v 23 Ta d tasɣart n ayt n Issakar, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, tineddam ak-d ředcur nsent.
\b
\m 
\v 24 \bd Taqedduḥt wiss xemsa\bd* tekkar as-dd i teqbič n ayt n \bd Acir\bd*, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\v 25 Aymir nsen aqa-t d Ḥalqa d Ḥali d Baṭan d Akcaf
\v 26 d Allammalak d Amɛad d Mic-Al, uca ittakkwaḍ ař \add wedrar n\add* Karmil di řɣarb u ař Cixur-Libna.
\v 27 Ittmeyyeř weymir ɣar manis dd-tneqqar tfuct ɣar Bayt-Dajun uca ittakkwaḍ ař Zabulun d teɣzurt n Yiftaḥ-Il ɣar ccamal, \add xenni ař\add* Bayt-Ɛamiq d Naɛiyil, uca itteffeɣ x uzeřmaḍ n Kabul
\v 28 uca \add iɛeddu ɣar\add* Ɛabrun d Raḥub d Ḥammun d Qana ař Ṣidun ameqqran.
\v 29 Ittmeyyeř weymir ɣar Rama iggur ař tandint n Ṣur i ifaryen u \add xenni\add* ittmeyyeř weymir ɣar Ḥuṣa u ṭṭrufa nnes ttakkwaḍen ař řebḥar, zi Ḥibl ař Akzib
\v 30 d Ɛumma d Afiq d Raḥub. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd tnayen u-ɛicrin n tneddam\bd* ak-d ředcur nsent.
\v 31 Ta d tasɣart n teqbič n ayt n Acir, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, tineddam-a ak-d ředcur nsent.
\b
\m 
\v 32 \bd Taqedduḥt wiss setta\bd* tekkar as-dd i ayt n \bd Naftali\bd*, i ayt n Naftali, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\v 33 Iɛeddu weymir nsen zi Ḥalaf, zi tcejjart n yigg di Ṣaɛanayim, d Adami-Naqib d Yabniyil ař Laqqum uca ṭṭrufa nnes ttakkwaḍen ař L’Urdun.
\v 34 Ittmeyyeř weymir ɣar řɣarb ɣar Aznut-Tabur u ssenni iɛeddu ɣar Ḥuquq u ittakkwaḍ ař Zabulun di ljanub u di řɣarb issuffuɣ ař Acir u di ccarq ař Yahuda \add ɣar\add* L’Urdun.
\v 35 Tineddam ifaryen aqa atent Ṣiddim d Ṣayr d Ḥammat d Raqqat d Kinnarat
\v 36 d Adama d Rama d Ḥaṣur
\v 37 d Qadac d Idřaɛi d Ɛayn-Ḥaṣur
\v 38 d Yirun d Mijdal-Il d Ḥurim d Bayt-Ɛanat d Bayt-Cams. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd tseɛṭac n tneddam\bd* ak-d ředcur nsent.
\v 39 Ta d tasɣart n ayt n Naftali, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, tineddam ak-d ředcur nsent.
\b
\m 
\v 40 \bd Taqedduḥt wiss sebɛa\bd* tekkar as-dd i teqbič n ayt n \bd Dan\bd*, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen.
\v 41 Aymir n tesɣart nsen aqa-t d Ṣurɛa d Icta’ul d Ɛir-Camc
\v 42 d Caɛalbim d Ayalun d Yitla,
\v 43 d Iylun d Timnata d Ɛaqrun
\v 44 d Iltaqay d Jibbatun d Baɛlat
\v 45 d Yahud d Bani-Baraq d Jat-Rimmun
\v 46 d Miyah-Yarqun d Raqqun ak-d temmurt qibač i Yafa.
\m 
\v 47 \add Maca\add* \bd tammurt n ayt n Dan teḥsar i nitni\bd*. Xenni geɛɛden ayt n Dan ɣar Lacam, arzmen amenɣi ak-d Lacam, řeɣben tt, wtin tt s řeqḍeɛ n ssif uca ṭṭfen tt \add d tasɣart nsen\add* uca qqimen zeddɣen din. Nitni ggin as i Lacam \add isem\add* Dan ɛlaḥsab isem n babatsen Dan.
\v 48 Ta d tasɣart n teqbič n ayt n Dan, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, tineddam-a ak-d ředcur nsent.
\b
\m 
\v 49 \add Umi\add* kemmřen ayt n Israil abeṭṭu n temmurt di tseqqar n řwart ɛlaḥsab iymiren nnes, wcin ayt n Israil uřa i Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, ict n tesɣart di řwesṭ nsen.
\v 50 Wcin as, s řumur n SIDI, tandint i tuɣa ittar, Timnat-Saraḥ x idurar n Ifrayim. Netta ibna tandint nni, uca iruḥ izdeɣ dinni.
\v 51 Tina d tiseqqar nni ittwabḍan \add d řwart\add* s tqedduḥt i ayt n Israil di Cilu zzat i wudem n SIDI ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar s ufus n ukehhan Aliɛazar d Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, d imɣaren \add n tudrin\add* n ibabaten n tqebbař. \add Ammu\add* kemmřen abeṭṭu n temmurt.
\b
\b
\c 20
\s1 Tineddam n tarewřa
\m 
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Yacuwa, inna:
\m 
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil, ini: ‘Ad tfarzem tineddam n tarewřa i yixef nwem, min xef d awem ssiwřeɣ s tsexxart n Musa, \f ◼ \fr 20:2 \fk s tsexxart n Musa\ft - s lḥarf: ‘s ufus n Musa’, ixs ad yini ‘s uqemmum n Musa’ niɣ ‘s řumur n Musa’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 20:2 \xt Uf. 21:13; Řxř. 35:6; Aɛwd. 19:1, 2\x*
\v 3 ḥima ad yarweř din uqettař nni inɣin ijj n bnadem zeg uweddar, břa ma ad as igg řeḥsab. Ad iřint d imucan mani ɣa tarewřem zeg uneqqam n idammen. \f ◼ \fr 20:3 \fk bnadem\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar’.\f*
\v 4 Mařa netta yarweř ɣar icten zi tneddam nni, ad ibedd ɣar tewwart n tendint uca ad iḥaja tamsart nnes deg imezzuɣen n imeqqranen n tendint. \add Xenni\add* ad t ssidfen di tendint, ad as wcen ijj n wemcan maḥend ad ɣarsen izdeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 20:4 \xt Řxř. 35:22, 23; Aɛwd. 19:4, 5\x*
\v 5 Mařa \add xenni\add* iḍfar i-t uneqqam n idammen, war d as tticen aqettař deg ufus nnes, maɣar netta inɣa jjar nnes břa ma ad as igg řeḥsab, tuɣa war t icarreh ca iḍennaḍ niɣ fariḍennaḍ.
\v 6 Netta ad iqqim izdeɣ di tendint nni, ař ɣa ibedd i řeḥkam zzat i wudem n tmesmunt, \add uca awarni man aya\add* ař ɣa immet arrays n ikehhanen wenni din iǧan deg wussan nni. Xenni izemmar uqettař ad iɛqeb ɣar tendint nnes u ɣar taddart nnes, ɣar tendint i zi dd-yarweř.
\m 
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* qeddsen Qadac deg idurar n Naftali di Ljalil u Cakim x idurar n Ifrayim u Qaryat-Arbaɛ, tenni d Ḥabrun, di Temmurt n Idurar n Yahuda.
\v 8 Aɣirin n L’Urdun, di jjihet n ccarq zi Ariḥa, wcin nitni zi teqbič n Rubin Baṣar di řexřa x řwaṭa \add yuɛřan\add* u zi teqbič n Jad \add wcin nitni\add* Ramut di Jilɛad u zi teqbič n Manassa \add tandint n\add* Julan di Bacan. \x ◘ \xo 20:8 \xt Aɛwd. 4:43\x*
\m 
\v 9 Tina d tineddam nni ittwaggen i marra ayt n Israil u i ubarrani nni i izeddɣen di řwesṭ nsen, ḥima kuř ijj zeg inni inɣin ijj n bnadem s uweddar, izemmar ad din yarweř, ḥima war ittmetti s ufus n ineqqamen n idammen ař ɣa ibedd i řḥukm zzat i wudem n tmesmunt. \f ◼ \fr 20:9 \fk bnadem\ft - di Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar’.\f*
\b
\b
\c 21
\s1 Tineddam n Ilawiyyen
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* qarrben-dd izeǧifen n \add tudrin n\add* ibabaten n Ilawiyyen ɣar ukehhan Aliɛazar d Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, u \add qarrben-dd\add* ɣar izeǧifen n \add tudrin n\add* ibabaten n tqebbař n ayt n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 21:1 \xt 1 Im. 6:39\x*
\v 2 Ssiwřen akidsen di Cilu di temmurt n Kenɛan, nnan: “SIDI yumur s ufus n Musa, ad aneɣ mmewcent tneddam, ḥima ad daysent nezdeɣ, ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa i řebhayem nneɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 21:2 \xt Řxř. 35\x*
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* wcin ayt n Israil s řumur n SIDI, zi tesɣart nsen, tineddam ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa i Ilawiyyen.
\b
\m 
\v 4 Uca tekkar asent-dd tqedduḥt i řaǧat n \bd Qahat\bd*. S tqedduḥt kkarent asen-dd i warraw n ukehhan Harun zeg Ilawiyyen \bd třeṭṭac n tneddam\bd* zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbič n Yahuda u n teqbič n Cimɛun u n teqbič n Binyamin.
\v 5 I inni iqqimen n ayt n Qahat \add kkarent asen-dd\add* s tqedduḥt ɛecra n tneddam zi \add temmurt n\add* řaǧat n teqbič n Ifrayim u n teqbič n Dan u n wezyen n teqbič n Manassa.
\m 
\v 6 I \bd ayt n Jarcun\bd* \add kkarent asen-dd\add* s tqedduḥt \bd třeṭṭac n tneddam\bd* zi \add temmurt n\add* řaǧat n teqbič n Issakar u n teqbič n Acir u n teqbič n Naftali u n wezyen n teqbič n Manassa di Bacan.
\m 
\v 7 I \bd ayt n Marari\bd* \add kkarent asen-dd s tqedduḥt\add* \bd tenɛac n tneddam\bd*, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbič n Rubin u n teqbič n Jad u n teqbič n Zabulun.
\v 8 Ayt n Israil wcin tineddam-a ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa s tqedduḥt i Ilawiyyen, am mammec \add t\add* yumur SIDI s tsexxart n Musa.
\b
\m 
\v 9 Zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbič n ayt n Yahuda u zi teqbič n ayt n Cimɛun wcin asen tineddam-a i ittwannan s yisem nsent
\v 10 u \add marra aya\add* ikkar asen-dd \bd i warraw n Harun \bdit nni iǧan\bdit* zi řaǧat n Iqahatiyyen\bd* zeg ayt n Lawi, minzi taqedduḥt tamezwarut tewḍa xasen.
\v 11 Nitni wcin asen tandint n Arbaɛ, babas n Ɛanaq, tenni d Ḥabrun, di Temmurt n Idurar n Yahuda ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa i d as dd-innḍen. \f ◼ \fr 21:11 \fk tandint n Arbaɛ\ft - niɣ ‘Qaryat-Arbaɛ’.\f*
\v 12 \add Maca\add* iyyaren n tendint d ředcur nnes wcin ten d agřa i Kalib, mmis n Yafunni.
\v 13 I ayt n ukehhan Harun wcin asen \add tineddam-a d\add* tandint n tarewřa i uqettař: Ḥabrun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Libna ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,
\v 14 d Yattir ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Ictumaɛ ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,
\v 15 d Ḥulun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Dabir ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,
\v 16 d Ɛayn ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Yuṭṭa ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Bayt-Cams ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, \add marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd tesɛa n tneddam\bd* zi tnayen n tqebbař-a.
\m 
\v 17 Zi teqbič n Binyamin \add wcin asen\add* Jibɛun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Jibɛa ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,
\v 18 Ɛanatut ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Ɛalmun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd arebɛa n tneddam\bd*.
\v 19 Marra tineddam n warraw n Harun, n ikehhanen, \add tuɣa atent di\add* \bd třeṭṭac n tneddam\bd* ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa.
\m 
\v 20 \bd I řaǧat n ayt n Qahat, Ilawiyyen, nni iqqimen zeg ayt n Qahat\bd* kkarent asen-dd s tqedduḥt tineddam zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbič n Ifrayim.
\v 21 Wcin asen \add tineddam-a d\add* tandint n tarewřa i uqettař: Cakim ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa x idurar n Ifrayim, d Jazar ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,
\v 22 d Qibṣayim ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Bayt-Ḥurun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd arebɛa n tneddam\bd*.
\m 
\v 23 Zi teqbič n Dan \add kkarent asen-dd:\add* Iltaqa ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, Jibbatun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,
\v 24 Ayalun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Jad-Rimmun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd arebɛa n tneddam\bd*.
\m 
\v 25 Zi \add temmurt n\add* wezyen n teqbič n Manassa \add kkarent asen-dd\add* Taɛnak ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Jad-Rimmun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd tnayen n tneddam\bd*.
\v 26 Marra tineddam i řaǧat n ayt n Qahat nni iqqimen \add tuɣa atent\add* di ɛecra n tneddam ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa.
\b
\m 
\v 27 Zi \add temmurt n\add* wezyen n teqbič n Manassa \add kkarent asen-dd tneddam-a\add* \bd i ayt n Jarcun\bd*, zi řaǧat n Ilawiyyen, am tendint n tarewřa i uqettař: Julan di Bacan ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Baɛactara ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* \add tuɣa atent di\add* \bd tnayen n tneddam\bd*.
\m 
\v 28 Zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbič n Issakar \add kkarent asen-dd:\add* Qicyun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Dabrat ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,
\v 29 Yarmut ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Ɛayn-Jannim ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* \add tuɣa atent di\add* \bd arebɛa n tneddam\bd*.
\m 
\v 30 Zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbič n Acir \add kkarent asen-dd:\add* Mic-Al ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Ɛabdun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,
\v 31 d Ḥalqat ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Raḥub ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* \add tuɣa atent di\add* \bd arebɛa n tneddam\bd*.
\m 
\v 32 Zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbič n Naftali \add kkarent asen-dd\add* am tendint n tarewřa i uqettař: Qadac di Ljalil ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Ḥammut-Dur ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Qartan ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* \add tuɣa atent\add* di \bd třata n tneddam\bd*.
\v 33 Marra tineddam n ayt n Jarcun ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen \add tuɣa atent di\add* třeṭṭac n tneddam ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa.
\b
\m 
\v 34 \bd I řaǧat n ayt n Marari\bd*, aqa aten d inni iqqimen \add ɛad\add* zeg Ilawiyyen, \add mmewcent asen\add* zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbič n Zabulun, Juqnaɛam ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, Qarta ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,
\v 35 Dimna ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Nahalal ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* tuɣa atent di \bd arebɛa n tneddam\bd*.
\m 
\v 36 Zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbič n Rubin \add kkarent asen-dd\add* Baṣar ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Yahṣa ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,
\v 37 Qadimut ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa d Mafaɛa ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* \add tuɣa atent di\add* \bd arebɛa n tneddam\bd*.
\m 
\v 38 Zi \add temmurt n\add* teqbič n Jad \add kkarent asen-dd\add* am tendint n tarewřa i uqettař: Ramut di Jilɛad ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Maḥanayim ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,
\v 39 Ḥacbun ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa, d Yaɛzir ak-d ddmani nnes n tarewsa. \add Marra jmiɛ\add* \add tuɣa atent di\add* \bd arebɛa n tneddam\bd*.
\m 
\v 40 \add Tuɣa tina\add* marra d tineddam i ayt n Marari, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nsen, tinni iqqimen zi řaǧat n Ilawiyyen, tinni x dd-tewḍa tqedduḥt nsen, \bdit marra jmiɛ tuɣa tent di\bdit* \bd tenɛac n tneddam\bd*.
\b
\m 
\v 41 \bd Marra tineddam\bd* di řwesṭ n řwart n ayt n Israil \add tuɣa atent di\add* \bd tmenya u-rebɛin n tneddam\bd* ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa.
\v 42 Tineddam-a tuɣa atent marra ak-d ddmani nsent n tarewsa i d asent innḍen. Ammu \add i tuɣa teǧa\add* ɣar marra tineddam-a.
\m 
\v 43 Ammu iwca SIDI i Israil marra tammurt nni tuɣa ijjuǧ ad tt iwc i řejdud nsen uca nitni warten tt uca ruḥen zeddɣen dayes.
\v 44 Uca SIDI igga asen řhudnet zi marra iɣezdisen, am mammec marra nni tuɣa ijjuǧ i řejdud nsen. Uřa d ijj zi řɛedyan nsen war d asen izemmar zzat i wudem nsen. SIDI iwca asen marra řɛedyan deg ufus nsen.
\v 45 Uřa d ijj n wawař zi marra awařen icnan i zi issiweř SIDI ɣar taddart n Israil iwḍa. Marra \add aya\add* ittwakemmeř.
\b
\b
\c 22
\s1 Aɛqab n tqebbař i iǧan ɣar ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun
\m 
\v 1 Xenni iřaɣa-dd Yacuwa i Irubiniyyen d Ijadiyyen d wezyen n teqbič n Manassa,
\v 2 inna asen: “Kenniw teḥḍam marra min xef i d awem yumur Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, u kenniw tesřam \add ɛawed\add* i tmijja inu di marra min xef d awem umureɣ. \x ◘ \xo 22:2 \xt Řxř. 32:20; Aɛwd. 3:18\x*
\v 3 Kenniw war tesmiḥem ca deg aytmatwem deg waṭṭas n wussan ař ass-a u teḥḍam aḥeṭṭu n řumur n SIDI, AREBBI nwem.
\v 4 Uca řexxu igga SIDI, AREBBI nwem, i aytmatwem arraḥet, am mammec tuɣa i d asen tt iwaɛd. Ɛeqbem xenni řexxu ɣar iqiḍan nwem di temmurt n řwart nwem nni d awem iwca Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun. \x ◘ \xo 22:4 \xt Řxř. 32:33; Aɛwd. 3:13; 29:8; Yac. 13:8\x*
\v 5 Maca ḥḍam mliḥ ad teggem řumur d Ccariɛa i d awem iwca Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, ḥima ad texsem SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ad tuyurem di marra ibriden nnes, ad teḥḍam marra řumurat nnes uca ad ɣares třeṣqem u ad as tsexxarem s marra wuř d marra řeɛmar nwem.” \x ◘ \xo 22:5 \xt Aɛwd. 10:12\x*
\m 
\v 6 Ibarek i-ten Yacuwa, ijja i-ten ad uyuren uca nitni areggʷḥen ɣar iqiḍan nsen.
\v 7 I wezyen n teqbič n Manassa tuɣa iwca Musa ict n tesɣart di Bacan, maca i yijj n wezyen nneɣni iwca as Yacuwa ict n tesɣart ɣar aytmatsen x uɣezdis-a n L’Urdun zi manis tɣeǧi tfuct. Umi ten issekk Yacuwa ɣar iqiḍan nsen, ibarek i-ten
\v 8 uca issiweř akidsen, inna: “S wagřa d ameqqran ad tɛeqbem ɣar iqiḍan nwem, s waṭṭas n řebhayem u s nnuqart d wureɣ u s nnḥas d wuzzař u s waṭṭas n warruḍ. Bḍam takeccaḍt n řɛedyan nwem ak-d aytmatwem.”
\v 9 Ɛeqben ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad d wezyen n teqbič n Manassa, ffɣen zi ɣar ayt n Israil, iggʷejjen x Cilu \add nni iǧan\add* di temmurt n Kenɛan, ḥima ad raḥen ɣar temmurt n Jilɛad, ɣar temmurt n řmuřk nsen nni iṭṭfen d agřa ɛlaḥsab řumur n SIDI s tsexxart n Musa.
\b
\s1 Aɛaltar n tqebbař ɣar ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun
\m 
\v 10 \add Umi\add* iwḍen nitni ɣar tmuwwa n L’Urdun nni \add iǧan ɛad\add* di temmurt n Kenɛan, bnan ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad d wezyen n teqbič n Manassa dinni ijj n uɛalṭar ɣar L’Urdun, ijj n uɛalṭar imɣar aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 22:10 \xt Yac. 18:7\x*
\v 11 Uca sřin ayt n Israil aqa qqaren: “Xzarem, ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad d wezyen n teqbič n Manassa bnan ijj n uɛalṭar ɣar weymir n temmurt n Kenɛan x tmuwwa n L’Urdun, x uɣezdis \add n L’Urdun\add* n ayt n Israil.”
\v 12 \add Umi\add* sřin ayt n Israil aya, tmun marra tmesmunt n ayt n Israil di Cilu ḥima ad ffɣen i umenɣi akidsen s ijj n řɛeskar.
\v 13 Uca ssekken ayt n Israil Finaḥas, mmis n ukehhan Aliɛazar, ɣar ayt n Rubin u ɣar ayt n Jad u ɣar wezyen n teqbič n Manassa di Jilɛad,
\v 14 u \add ssekken\add* akides ɛecra n řḥukkam, ijj n řḥakem zi kuř taddart n babas, zi marra tiqebbař n Israil. Kuř ijj \add zzaysen\add* tuɣa d azeǧif n taddart n řejdud nsen i řuřuf n Israil.
\m 
\v 15 Usin-dd nitni ɣar ayt n Rubin u ɣar ayt n Jad u ɣar wezyen n teqbič n Manassa di temmurt n Jilɛad, nnan asen:
\v 16 “Ammu i tessiweř marra tmesmunt n SIDI: Min ixs ad yini řeɣdar-a i zi teɣdarem AREBBI n Israil umi tḥeyydem ass-a zi ḍeffar n SIDI, umi tebnam i yixef nwem ijj n uɛalṭar maḥend ad tɣewwɣem x SIDI ass-a?
\v 17 Ma war iǧi cfa aneɣ řmuɛṣiyyet n Faɣur, \add řmuɛṣiyyet i zi\add* ɣar ass-a \add ɛad\add* war nettwassizdeg u zzayes i tewḍa jjriḥect x tmesmunt n SIDI?\x ◘ \xo 22:17 \xt Řxř. 25:3; Aɛwd. 4:3\x*
\v 18 Ma aqa kenniw ass-a tewcim s weɛrur i SIDI uca ad imsar \add xenni\add*, umi ɣa tɣewwɣem ass-a x SIDI, ad iffugem Netta x marra tmesmunt n Israil?
\v 19 Mařa zeɛma texmej temmurt i iǧan d agřa nwem, \add xenni\add* ɛdum ɣar temmurt nni iǧan d agřa n SIDI u mani teǧa Tzeddiɣt n SIDI uca ksim i yixef nwem ijj n wegra di řwesṭ nneɣ, \add maca\add* war tɣewwɣem ca x SIDI u war tɣewwɣem ca xaneɣ umi ɣa tebnam ijj n uɛalṭar i yixef nwem, mɣir aɛalṭar n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ.
\v 20 Ma tuɣa Ɛaxan, mmis n Zaraḥ, war iɣdar di tmesřact n min ittwaḥarrmen \add i uteḥḥi\add* u xenni ma war dd-ittis uduqqez n weɣḍab x marra tamesmunt n Israil? Uca aryaz nni war immut weḥḥḍes waha di řmuɛṣiyyet nnes.’”
\m 
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* arrin-dd ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad d wezyen n teqbič n Manassa uca ssiwřen ak-d izeǧifen x řuřuf n Israil:
\v 22 “Arebbi x \add marra\add* irebbiten, SIDI, Arebbi x \add marra\add* irebbiten issen \add i-t\add* u Israil ad \add t\add* issen \add ɛawed\add*! Mařa iffeɣ-dd aya zeg uɣewweɣ niɣ zi řeɣdar x SIDI, \add xenni\add* war xaneɣ tceṭṭar ca ass-a, \x ◘ \xo 22:22 \xt Izhd. 50:1\x*
\v 23 \add mařa tuɣa\add* ḥima ad nebna i neccin ijj n uɛalṭar maḥend ad newc s weɛrur i SIDI niɣ \add mařa tuɣa\add* ḥima ad nqeddem ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ niɣ ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* niɣ i usewjed n tɣarṣa n řehna, ejj SIDI simant nnes ad \add t\add* ibeqqec.
\v 24 \add Uct xaneɣ\add*, mařa war neggi aya zeg wemnus umi neqqar: ‘Iḥenjiren nwem \add zemmaren\add* ad inin i iḥenjiren nneɣ tiwecca: Min jar awem-dd ak-d SIDI, AREBBI n Israil?
\v 25 SIDI igga L’Urdun d aymir jar aneɣ d kenniw, ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad! Kenniw war ɣarwem ca tasɣart di SIDI!’ \add Ammu\add* zemmaren ad ssbedden iḥenjiren nwem iḥenjiren nneɣ x tiggʷudi n SIDI.
\v 26 \add X uyenni\add* nenna: Ejj aneɣ ad nebna aɛalṭar-a, war iǧi i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ uřa i tɣarṣt,
\v 27 \add maca\add* ḥima ad yiři d acehhad jar neccin d kenniw u jar jjiřat nneɣ awarni aneɣ, ḥima ad nsexxar di tsexxart n SIDI zzat i wudem nnes s tɣarṣi nneɣ n wecmaḍ d tɣarṣi nneɣ \add nneɣni\add* d tɣarṣi nneɣ n řehna u ḥima iḥenjiren nwem war qqaren i iḥenjiren nneɣ: Kenniw war ɣarwem ca tasɣart di SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 22:27 \xt Amz. 31:48; Yac. 24:27\x*
\v 28 Neccin nenna: Mařa imsar tiwecca ad inin nitni aya i neccin u i jjiřat \add awarni aneɣ\add*, xenni ad nini: ‘Xzarem, amedya n řebni n uɛalṭar-a n SIDI nni iggin řejdud nneɣ, war iǧi i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ niɣ i tɣarṣt \add nneɣni\add*, \add maca\add* ḥima ad yiři d acehhad jar neccin d kenniw.’
\v 29 Iggʷej xaneɣ aqa neccin ad nɣewweɣ x SIDI niɣ ass-a ad newc s weɛrur i SIDI umi ɣa nebna ijj n uɛalṭar i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ niɣ i tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* niɣ i tɣarṣt \add nneɣni\add*, illa aɛalṭar n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, wenni iǧan zzat i Tzeddiɣt nnes.”
\m 
\v 30 Akehhan Finaḥas d řḥukkam n tmesmunt d izeǧifen x řuřuf n Israil nni kides \add iǧan\add*, sřin awařen i issiwřen ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad d ayt n Manassa u tuɣa aya d lemliḥ di tiṭṭawin nsen.
\v 31 Finaḥas, mmis n Aliɛazar, inna i ayt n Rubin u i ayt n Jad u i ayt n Manassa: “Ass-a ad tessnem belli SIDI aqa-t di řwesṭ nneɣ umi kenniw war teɣdarem ca SIDI. S uya kenniw tfekkem ayt n Israil zeg ufus n SIDI.”
\m 
\v 32 \add Xenni\add* yareggʷeḥ ukehhan Finaḥas, mmis n Aliɛazar, ak-d řḥukkam zeg ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad, zi temmurt n Jilɛad ɣar temmurt n Kenɛan, ɣar ayt n Israil, uca nitni ggin daysen řexbar.
\v 33 Tuɣa tamesřact d lemliḥ di tiṭṭawin n ayt n Israil uca ḥemden ayt n Israil AREBBI u war d asen nnan ɛad ad ffɣen ad mmenɣen maḥend ad areddǧen tammurt i di tuɣa zeddɣen ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad.
\v 34 Ayt n Rubin d ayt n Jad řaɣan as i uɛalṭar nni: “Ad yiři d acehhad jar aneɣ aqa SIDI d AREBBI.”
\b
\b
\c 23
\s1 Awař n Yacuwa i izeǧifen n Israil
\m 
\v 1 Imsar umi ɛdun aṭṭas n wussan awarni umi SIDI tuɣa igga i Israil řhudnet zi marra řɛedyan nnes i d as dd-innḍen u umi tuɣa Yacuwa iwsar, imɣar deg wussan,
\v 2 aqa iřaɣa Yacuwa i marra Israil, imɣaren nnes d izeǧifen nnes d řquḍat nnes d imeḥḍayen nnes, inna asen: “Necc wsareɣ u mɣareɣ deg wussan
\v 3 uca kenniw teẓrim marra min igga SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ak-d marra řegnus-a zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem, maɣar SIDI, AREBBI nwem Simant nnes, d wenni tuɣa immenɣen di ṭṭweɛ nwem.
\v 4 Xzar necc bḍiɣ awem řegnus-a i iqqimen jar awem s tqedduḥt, am tesɣart \add n řwart\add* i tqebbař nwem, ak-d marra řegnus i teḥḥiɣ zi L’Urdun ař řebḥar ameqqran mani tɣeǧi tfuct.
\v 5 SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ad xasen ibarrez zzat i wudem nwem u ad xasen yaẓẓeř zzat i wudem nwem zi řwart nsen u kenniw ad tᵉṭṭfem tammurt nsen d řwart, am mammec i d awem issiweř SIDI, AREBBI nwem. \x ◘ \xo 23:5 \xt Uf. 14:14; 23:27; Řxř. 33:53; Aɛwd. 6:19; Yac. 13:6\x*
\v 6 Ḥḍam aṭṭas s jjehd u ggem marra min yurin deg wedlis-a ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa n Musa, ḥima war xas tḥeyyidem uřa \add ɣar\add* yefus uřa \add ɣar\add* uzeřmaḍ, \x ◘ \xo 23:6 \xt Aɛwd. 5:32; 28:14\x*
\v 7 ḥima kenniw war ttṣuram ixef nwem ak-d řegnus-a inni \add ɛad\add* iqqimen ɣarwem, u war ttfekkarem \add ɛad\add* deg yisem n irebbiten nsen u war \add xasen\add* ttjaǧam u \add ḥima\add* kenniw war d asen tɛebbdem u war d asen tᵉttbendqem. \x ◘ \xo 23:7 \xt Uf. 23:13; Izhd. 16:4; Irm. 5:7; Ṣaf. 1:5; Afa. 5:3\x*
\v 8 Maɣar ittxeṣṣa ad třeṣqem i SIDI, AREBBI nwem, am mammec i t teggim ař ass-a. \x ◘ \xo 23:8 \xt Aɛwd. 11:22\x*
\v 9 SIDI yuẓẓeř x řegnus mɣaren u jjehden zzat i wudem nwem. U xawem kenniw, ař ass-a war din ḥed i izemmaren ad ibedd zzat i wudem nwem.
\v 10 Ijj n weryaz zzaywem izemmar ad yaẓẓeř x wařef \add n yeryazen\add*, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nwem Simant nnes, d wenni ittmenɣan di ṭṭweɛ nwem, am mammec tuɣa akidwem issiweř. \x ◘ \xo 23:10 \xt Lawi 26:8; Aɛwd. 32:30\x*
\v 11 Ḥḍam \add xenni\add* ař ṭṭarf x řeɛmur nwem ḥima ad texsem SIDI, AREBBI nwem.
\v 12 Minzi mařa kenniw tḥeyydem xas uřa d ict n jjurret \add waha\add*, uca ad třeṣqem i min kidwem iqqimen \add ɛad\add* n řegnus, i yinni kiwem iqqimen, uca ad tdewřem d iḍeggʷařen u ad ɣarsen tadfem u nitni am nneɣni,
\v 13 xenni ad tessnem nican, aqa SIDI, AREBBI nwem, war ittiẓẓeř ɛad x řegnus-a zzat i wudem nwem. Nitni ad dewřen d řfex d tracca i kenniw, d \add tiyyita s\add* urekkuḍ x iɣezdisen nwem d isennanen i tiṭṭawin nwem, ař ɣa tᵉttwateḥḥam zi temmurt taṣebḥant i d awem iwca SIDI, AREBBI nwem.
\v 14 Xzar, ass-a necc simant inu ad uyureɣ abrid n marra tammurt u kenniw ad tessnem s marra uř nwem u s marra řeɛmar nwem, aqa uřa d ijj n wawař zi marra awařen i xawem inna SIDI, AREBBI nwem, war dd-iffiɣ. Marra ffɣen-dd xawem, uřa d ijj n wawař war iqqim war dd-iffiɣ.
\v 15 Uca ad imsar, am mammec xawem dd-yusa marra awař icnan i kidwem issiweř SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ammu i xawem i ɣa isseqfeř SIDI uřa d kuř awař iɛeffnen ař Netta kenniw iteḥḥa zi temmurt-a taṣebḥant i d awem iwca SIDI, AREBBI nwem.
\v 16 Mařa kenniw tɛeddam x Řɛahd n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, \add Řɛahd\add* nni x d awem yumur Netta uca kenniw ad tuyurem ad tɛebdem i irebbiten nneɣni uca ad asen tuḍarem, \add xenni\add* ad xawem yareɣ weɣḍab n SIDI uca kenniw ad tᵉttwateḥḥam deɣya zi temmurt taṣebḥant i d awem iwca Netta.
\b
\b
\c 24
\s1 Tajdid n Řɛahd n Israil ak-d SIDI
\m 
\v 1 Yacuwa issmun marra tiqebbař n Israil di Cakim uca iřaɣa i imɣaren n Israil d izeǧifen nsen d řquḍat nsen d imeḥḍayen nsen uca nitni ssbedden ixef nsen zzat i wudem n AREBBI.
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inna Yacuwa i marra řgens: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Řejdud nwem zeddɣen zi cḥař uya x ujemmaḍ n yeɣẓar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, Taraḥ, babas n Ibrahim d babas n Naḥur, u nitni tuɣa ttsexxaren i irebbiten nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 24:2 \xt Amz. 11:26, 31; Aɛwd. 26:5\x*
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* iwyeɣ-dd jedditwem Ibrahim zeg uɣirin i iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add* u jjiɣ t yuyur di marra tammurt n Kenɛan. Necc arniɣ i zzariɛet nnes u wciɣ as Isḥaq. \x ◘ \xo 24:3 \xt Amz. 12:1, 21:2\x*
\v 4 I Isḥaq wciɣ Yaɛqub d Ɛisu, u i Ɛisu wciɣ \add tammurt n\add* idurar n Saɛir d tasɣart, \add maca\add* Yaɛqub d iḥenjiren nnes hwan ɣar Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 24:4 \xt Amz. 25:24, 36:8, 46:1\x*
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* ssekkeɣ Musa d Harun uca wtiɣ Miṣra am mammec \add t\add* ggiɣ di řwesṭ nnes u awarni as ssuffɣeɣ-dd kenniw. \x ◘ \xo 24:5 \xt Uf. 3:10-4:17; 12:37\x*
\v 6 Necc ssuffɣeɣ-dd řejdud nwem zi Miṣra u kenniw tiwḍem-dd ɣar řebḥar u Imiṣriyyen ḍfaren ibabaten nwem s ikarruten d imnayen ař Řebḥar n Telga. \x ◘ \xo 24:6 \xt Uf. 14:1\x*
\v 7 Uca sɣuyen ɣar SIDI u Netta igga taǧest jar awem d Imiṣriyyen uca ijja řebḥar issfeyyeḍ xasen ařami ten idřa. S tiṭṭawin nwem teẓrim min ggiɣ di Miṣra. \add Awarni aya\add* tuɣa tzeddɣem aṭṭas n wussan di řexřa.
\v 8 Necc iwyeɣ-dd kenniw ɣar temmurt n Imuriyyen i tuɣa izeddɣen aɣirin i L’Urdun. Nitni mmenɣen akidwem, \add maca\add* Necc ggiɣ ten deg ufus nwem u kenniw tᵉṭṭfem tammurt nsen u Necc qḍiɣ xasen zzat i wudem nwem. \x ◘ \xo 24:8 \xt Řxř. 21:21, 33\x*
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Balak, mmis n Saffur, ajeǧid n Mu’ab, uca immneɣ ak-d Israil. Netta issekk ḥima ad řaɣan i Bilɛam, mmis n Baɛur, maḥend ad kenniw inɛeř.
\v 10 \add Maca\add* Necc war xseɣ ad sřeɣ i Balɛam. \add S uya\add* ibarek netta i kenniw aṭṭas u Necc fekkeɣ-dd kenniw zeg ufus nnes.
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* teẓwam L’Urdun, tusim-dd ɣar Ariḥa. Imezdaɣ n Ariḥa, mmenɣen akidwem, Imuriyyen d Ifiriziyyen d ayt n Kenɛan d Iḥittiyyen d Ijirjasiyyen d Iḥiwiyyen d Iyabusiyyen uca wciɣ awem ten deg ufus nwem. \x ◘ \xo 24:11 \xt Yac. 3:14; 6:1, 20; 10:8; 11:8\x*
\v 12 Necc ssekkeɣ irezzan iḍarɣařen uca uẓẓřen xasen zzatwem, \add am mammec ttwaẓẓřen\add* tnayen n ijeǧiden nni zzat i wudem nwem. \add D man aya\add* war iǧi s ssif nwem uřa s řqews nwem. \x ◘ \xo 24:12 \xt Uf. 23:28; Aɛwd. 7:20; Izhd. 44:4\x*
\v 13 Necc wciɣ awem tammurt i x war tarebrem u tineddam nni war tebnim, ḥima ad tzeddɣem daysent. Uca teccim \add ɛawed\add* zi tzayarin d izemmuren i tuɣa war teẓẓum.’\x ◘ \xo 24:13 \xt Aɛwd. 6:10, 11, 12\x*
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, ggʷedem SIDI uca sexxarem as s řekmaret d řaman. Nḍarem irebbiten nni umi sexxaren řejdud nwem aɣirin i iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add* u di Miṣra uca sexxarem i SIDI.
\v 15 \add Maca\add* mařa war dd-tusi x tiṭṭawin nwem maḥend ad tsexxarem i SIDI, xenni ixḍarem ass-a i man wen umi i ɣa tsexxarem, i irebbiten nni umi sexxaren řejdud nwem aɣirin i iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, niɣ i irebbiten n Imuriyyen nni di temmurt nsen tzeddɣem. Necc maca d taddart inu, neccin ad nsexxar i SIDI!”
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd řgens: “Man aya iggʷej aneɣ, aqa neccin ad nejj SIDI ad nexdem irebbiten nneɣni.
\v 17 Maɣar SIDI d AREBBI nneɣ d Netta i d aneɣ-dd issgeɛɛden zi temmurt n Miṣra, neccin d řejdud nneɣ, zi taddart n tesmuɣi u Netta d wenni iggin řeɛřamat timeqqranin zzat i tiṭṭawin nneɣ u Netta issřeqqa xaneɣ di marra abrid i nuyur u jar marra řegnus i umi ncuq \add tammurt nsen\add*.
\v 18 SIDI yuẓẓeř x marra řegnus zzat i wudem nneɣ, uřa x Imuriyyen, imezdaɣ n temmurt. Uřa d neccin ad nsexxar i SIDI, maɣar Netta d AREBBI nneɣ.”
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* inna Yacuwa i řgens: “Kenniw war tzemmarem ad tsexxarem i SIDI, maɣar Netta d AREBBI Amqeddes aṭṭas u Netta d ijj n Arebbi ittasmen. Netta war d awem iɣeffar ixeṭṭan nwem d ddnub nwem.
\v 20 Mařa kenniw tejjim SIDI, ad tsexxarem i irebbiten nneɣni, \add xenni\add* Netta ad xawem inneqřeb, ad d awem igg řɣar uca ad kenniw iqḍa, awarni řami Netta igga akidwem \add qbeř\add* taṣebḥant.” \x ◘ \xo 24:20 \xt Yac. 23:15\x*
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* inna řgens i Yacuwa: “Lla, minzi neccin ad nsexxar i SIDI.”
\v 22 Inna Yacuwa i řgens: “Kenniw d řechud x ixef nwem, aqa kenniw tfarzem SIDI, ḥima ad as tsexxarem.” Nitni nnan “\add Neccin\add* d řechud!”
\v 23 “\add Xenni\add* řexxu, nḍarem irebbiten iɣriben nni \add iǧan\add* di řwesṭ nwem u tarrem uřawen nwem ɣar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil!”
\v 24 Inna řgens i Yacuwa: “Neccin ad nsexxar i SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, uca ad nseř i tmijja nnes.”
\v 25 Deg wass nni igga Yacuwa ijj n řɛahd ak-d řgens uca igga asen di Cakim tawṣeyyet d lfariḍa. \x ◘ \xo 24:25 \xt Uf. 15:25\x*
\v 26 Yura Yacuwa awařen-a deg wedlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa n SIDI uca netta iksi ijj n weẓru d ameqqran uca issbedd i-t di Cakim sadu ict n tcejjart n yigg nni ibedden ɣar Zzawect Iqeddsen n SIDI.
\v 27 Inna Yacuwa i marra řgens: “Xzarem, aẓru-ya ad xaneɣ yiři d acehhad, minzi netta isřa marra awařen n SIDI nni kidneɣ issiweř u netta ad yiři d acehhad i kenniw ḥima war ttɣeccam AREBBI nwem.”
\v 28 \add Xenni\add* yarxu Yacuwa i řgens, kuř aryaz \add iruḥ\add* ɣar tesɣart nnes.
\b
\s1 Řmewt n Yacuwa d Aliɛazir
\m 
\v 29 Awarni i tmesřayin-a imsar, belli Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, amsexxar n SIDI, immut, netta d ijj n mmis \add n bnadem\add* ɣares mya u-ɛecra n iseggʷusa.
\v 30 Neḍřen t di temmurt n tesɣart nnes di Timnat-Saraḥ nni iǧan x idurar n Ifrayim, ɣar ccamal n wedrar n Jaɛac. \x ◘ \xo 24:30 \xt Yac. 19:50; Řqḍ. 2:9\x*
\v 31 Israil isexxar i SIDI marra ussan n Yacuwa d marra ussan n imɣaren nni iqqimen ddaren ict n řweqt d azirar awarni i Yacuwa u ssnen marra min igga SIDI di ṭṭweɛ n Israil.
\v 32 Ixsan n Yusuf i tuɣa dd-iwyen akidsen ayt n Israil zi Miṣra, neḍřen ten di Cakim di tkirat n yeyyar i tuɣa isɣa Yaɛqub x ayt n Ḥamur, babas n Cakim, s mya n i iziynat n nnuqart iweznen uca tedweř d tasɣart n ayt n Yusuf. \x ◘ \xo 24:32 \xt Amz. 33:18-20; Amz. 50:25; Uf. 13:19\x*
\v 33 Uřa d Aliɛazar, mmis n Harun, immut uca neḍřen t di tewrirt n mmis n Finaḥas, \add tawrirt\add* i d as immewcen \add i Finaḥas\add* deg idurar n Ifrayim. 
